inst data corruption. (<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/en.wikipedia.org\\/wiki\\/Cyclic_redundancy_check\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\">Wikipedia<\\/a>)<\\/p><p>I wrote a VHDL code to simulate user input as a number of bits and shows the output with the CRC code attached on the LEDs of the intel DE2-70<\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"},{\"id\":\"c81f681\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/waseemorphali.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2019\\/03\\/CRC1-Diagram.png\",\"id\":205},\"caption_source\":\"custom\",\"caption\":\"Implementation of CRC-3\",\"_background_color\":\"#ffffff\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"},{\"id\":\"18ae4d2\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/waseemorphali.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2019\\/03\\/CRC0-Diagram.png\",\"id\":206},\"caption_source\":\"custom\",\"caption\":\"Implementation of CRC-5\",\"width\":{\"unit\":\"%\",\"size\":82}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"},{\"id\":\"e4573a2\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/waseemorphali.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2019\\/03\\/CRC2-Diagram.png\",\"id\":207},\"caption_source\":\"custom\",\"caption\":\"Implementation of CRC-8\",\"width\":{\"unit\":\"%\",\"size\":100}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"},{\"id\":\"3b1a8ec\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p>I simulated the circuit using the software from Intel called Quartus and showed how it works perfectly as inteded:<\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"},{\"id\":\"e7f701b\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/waseemorphali.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2019\\/03\\/crc0-simulation.jpg\",\"id\":221},\"caption_source\":\"custom\",\"caption\":\"crc0 shows the CRC-3 code to be attached\",\"width\":{\"unit\":\"%\",\"size\":100}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"},{\"id\":\"e48e774\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":