\/p>\",\"_id\":\"e0e4521\"},{\"tab_title\":\"Power System Design and Analysis\",\"tab_content\":\"<p>May 2015<\\/p><p><span class=\\\"fontstyle0\\\">Learned how to use ETAP software and designed a simple power network and analyzed it.<\\/span> <\\/p>\",\"_id\":\"39efa38\"}]},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"accordion\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"2e1a31a\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"2b726ec\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"2114164\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"spacer\"},{\"id\":\"51284d3\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"title\":\"Skills\",\"title_color\":\"rgba(0,0,0,0.99)\",\"typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"typography_font_family\":\"Arial\",\"link\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/waseemorphali.com\\/projects\\/\",\"is_external\":\"\",\"nofollow\":\"\"}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"heading\"},{\"id\":\"6a52681\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"structure\":\"20\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"2ded8ee\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":50,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"3327f42\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<ul><li><span class=\\\"fontstyle0\\\">Microsoft Office Suite<\\/span><\\/li><li><span class=\\\"fontstyle0\\\">C<\\/span><\\/li><li><span class=\\\"fontstyle0\\\">Python<\\/span><\\/li><li><span class=\\\"fontstyle0\\\">Matlab<\\/span><\\/li><li><span class=\\\"fontstyle0\\\">Assembly<\\/span><\\/li><li><span class=\\\"fontstyle0\\\">VHDL<\\/span><\\/li><\\/ul>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":true},{\"id\":\"a14fa1c\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":50,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"4c82420\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<ul><li><span class=\\\"fontstyle0\\\">Mentor Graphics<\\/span><\\/li><li><span class=\\\"fontstyle0\\\">HSPICE<\\/span><\\/li><li>PLC Programming<\\/li><li><span class=\\\"fontstyle0\\\">Arduino<\\/span><\\/li><li>Fusion 360<\\/li><li><span class=\\\"fontstyle0\\\">Languages: English, Arabic, Spanish (elementary)<\\/span><\\/li><\\/ul>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":true}],\"isInner\":true}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false}]'),(1375,278,'_elementor_version','0.4'),(1376,278,'_elementor_edit_mode','builder'),(1438,287,'_menu_item_target',''),(1439,287,'_menu_item_classes','a:1:{i:0;s:0:\"\";}'),(1387,279,'_elementor_edit_mode','builder'),(1388,279,'_elementor_template_type','post'),(1389,279,'_wp_page_template','default'),(1390,279,'_elementor_data','[{\"id\":\"406ff57\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"069c4c9\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"ec660f4\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p>A\\u00a0<b>cyclic redundancy check<\\/b>\\u00a0(<b>CRC<\\/b>) is an\\u00a0error-detecting code\\u00a0commonly used in digital\\u00a0networks\\u00a0and storage devices to detect accidental changes to raw data. Blocks of data entering these systems get a short\\u00a0<i>check value<\\/i>\\u00a0attached, based on the remainder of a\\u00a0polynomial division\\u00a0of their contents. On retrieval, the calculation is repeated and, in the event the check values do not match, corrective action can be taken against data corruption. (<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/en.wikipedia.org\\/wiki\\/Cyclic_redundancy_check\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\">Wikipedia<\\/a>)<\\/p><p>I wrote a VHDL code to simulate user input as a number of bits and shows the output with the CRC code attached on the LEDs of the intel DE2-70<\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"},{\"id\":\"c81f681\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/waseemorphali.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2019\\/03\\/CRC1-Diagram.png\",\"id\":205},\"caption_source\":\"custom\",\"caption\":\"Implementation of CRC-3\",\"_background_color\":\"#ffffff\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"},{\"id\":\"18ae4d2\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/waseemorphali.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2019\\/03\\/CRC0-Diagram.png\",\"id\":206},\"caption_source\":\"custom\",\"caption\":\"Implementation of CRC-5\",\"width\":{\"unit\":\"%\",\"size\":82}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"},{\"id\":\"e4573a2\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/waseemorphali.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2019\\/03\\/CRC2-Diagram.png\",\"id\":207},\"caption_source\":\"custom\",\"caption\":\"Implementation of CRC-8\",\"width\":{\"unit\":\"%\",\"size\":100}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"},{\"id\":\"3b1a8ec\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p>I simulated the circuit using the software from Intel called Quartus and showed how it works perfectly as inteded:<\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"},{\"id\":\"e7f701b\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/waseemorphali.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2019\\/03\\/crc0-simulation.jpg\",\"id\":221},\"caption_source\":\"custom\",\"caption\":\"crc0 shows the CRC-3 code to be attached\",\"width\":{\"unit\":\"%\",\"size\":100}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"},{\"id\":\"e48e774\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/waseemorphali.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2019\\/03\\/crc1-simulation.jpg\",\"id\":222},\"caption_source\":\"custom\",\"caption\":\"crc1 shows the CRC-5 code to be attached\",\"width\":{\"unit\":\"%\",\"size\":100}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"},{\"id\":\"68db586\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/waseemorphali.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2019\\/03\\/crc2-simulation.jpg\",\"id\":223},\"caption_source\":\"custom\",\"caption\":\"crc2 shows the CRC-8 code to be attached\",\"width\":{\"unit\":\"%\",\"size\":100}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"},{\"id\":\"2dfa1e4\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p>I presented the circuit and code to the professor and demonstrated the how the code works on the DE2-70 board<\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"},{\"id\":\"2e6bb89\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/waseemorphali.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2019\\/03\\/20181217_115414.jpg\",\"id\":220}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false}]'),(1391,279,'_elementor_version','0.4'),(1392,279,'_elementor_css','a:4:{s:4:\"time\";i:1552617637;s:5:\"fonts\";a:0:{}s:6:\"status\";s:4:\"file\";i:0;s:0:\"\";}'),(1412,283,'_menu_item_type','post_type'),(1413,283,'_menu_item_menu_item_parent','0'),(1414,283,'_menu_item_object_id','11'),(1415,283,'_menu_item_object','page'),(1416,283,'_menu_item_target',''),(1417,283,'_menu_item_classes','a:1:{i:0;s:0:\"\";}'),(1418,283,'_menu_item_xfn',''),(1419,283,'_menu_item_url',''),(1437,287,'_menu_item_object','custom'),(1436,287,'_menu_item_object_id','287'),(1432,286,'_elementor_version','0.4'),(1433,286,'_elementor_edit_mode','builder'),(1434,287,'_menu_item_type','custom'),(1435,287,'_menu_item_menu_item_parent','0'),(1431,286,'_elementor_data','[{\"id\":\"912d426\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"845857d\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"7e3adbd\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"title\":\"Education\",\"title_color\":\"rgba(0,0,0,0.99)\",\"typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"typography_font_family\":\"Arial\",\"link\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/waseemorphali.com\\/education\\/\",\"is_external\":\"\",\"nofollow\":\"\"}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"heading\"},{\"id\":\"f9ad5d4\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"structure\":\"20\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"f8e4df6\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":50},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"a2e1690\",\"elTyp