itor\":\"<p><strong>Jan 2011 - Dec 2015<\\/strong><\\/p><p><strong>GPA: 3.12 \\/ 4<\\/strong><\\/p>\",\"align\":\"center\",\"_padding\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"14\",\"right\":\"0\",\"bottom\":\"0\",\"left\":\"0\",\"isLinked\":false}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"22cbb2c\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"structure\":\"20\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"7c33585\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":50,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"9a7b338\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p><strong>High Level Courses:<\\/strong><\\/p><ul><li><strong>PLC Programming:<\\/strong> Learned programming Siemens PLCs using ladder programming.<\\/li><li><strong>Process Control:\\u00a0<\\/strong>PID controllers and linear systems.<\\/li><li><strong>Power System Analysis:\\u00a0<\\/strong>Used ETAP software to design and analyse power system.<\\/li><li><strong>Telecommunication Networks<\\/strong><\\/li><li><strong>Analogue Communication Electronics<\\/strong><\\/li><\\/ul>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"abf0ce9\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":50,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"9633634\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/waseemorphali.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2019\\/01\\/download.png\",\"id\":107},\"image_size\":\"thumbnail\",\"link_to\":\"custom\",\"link\":{\"url\":\"www.kfupm.edu.sa\\/\",\"is_external\":\"on\",\"nofollow\":\"\"},\"_padding\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"35\",\"right\":\"0\",\"bottom\":\"0\",\"left\":\"0\",\"isLinked\":false}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"aa1b2f7\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"fcb34e3\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false}]'),(1526,306,'_elementor_version','0.4'),(1527,117,'_elementor_css','a:4:{s:4:\"time\";i:1577749734;s:5:\"fonts\";a:0:{}s:6:\"status\";s:4:\"file\";i:0;s:0:\"\";}'),(1528,307,'_edit_lock','1577753341:1'),(1529,307,'_elementor_edit_mode','builder'),(1530,307,'_elementor_template_type','post'),(1531,309,'_elementor_edit_mode','builder'),(1532,309,'_elementor_template_type','post'),(1533,310,'_elementor_edit_mode','builder'),(1534,310,'_elementor_template_type','post'),(1535,310,'_wp_page_template','default'),(1536,310,'_elementor_data','[{\"id\":\"dfaa647\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"ed9ac74\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"53bd2ef\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p>We implemented an algorithm for tree pattern matching described in the IEEE paper \\\"<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/ieeexplore.ieee.org\\/document\\/1598158\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\">A Parallel Algorithm and Architecture for Object Recognition in Images<\\/a>\\\".<br \\/>We used VHDL to implement the algorithm, and we added our own designed components to control data flow through the circuit. The team consisted of 4 students, I was the leader of the group.<\\/p><p>We used ModelSim to simulate and test the VHDL code.<\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"},{\"id\":\"4ee7213\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/waseemorphali.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2019\\/03\\/complete-diagram.png\",\"id\":231},\"caption_source\":\"custom\",\"caption\":\"System block diagram\",\"width\":{\"unit\":\"%\",\"size\":82}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"},{\"id\":\"4d574a6\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p>The system proposed in the paper uses processing elements (PEs) to process the data serially and send the result back, we designed and added memory blocks that handle data input and a controller to handle data distribution and control of the different PEs and registers. The detailed diagrams of the top and bottom parts of the system are shown below.<\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"},{\"id\":\"03299d8\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/waseemorphali.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2019\\/03\\/top-part-diagram.png\",\"id\":233},\"caption_source\":\"custom\",\"caption\":\"Top part\",\"width\":{\"unit\":\"%\",\"size\":77}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"},{\"id\":\"71f3c9b\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/waseemorphali.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2019\\/03\\/bottom-part-diagram.png\",\"id\":234},\"caption_source\":\"custom\",\"caption\":\"Bottom part\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"},{\"id\":\"55fcf1a\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p>The controller is built using a state machine whose diagram is shown below.<\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"},{\"id\":\"bc13b9e\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/waseemorphali.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2019\\/03\\/State-Diagram.png\",\"id\":236}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"},{\"id\":\"5b84953\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p>In the end, we delivered a good system inspired by the paper and designed by us. Also, I gained very good experience in VHDL, and in working as part of a team on a challenging project.<\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"},{\"id\":\"4acf407\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/waseemorphali.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2019\\/03\\/20180508_210023.jpg\",\"id\":240}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false}]'),(1537,310,'_elementor_version','0.4'),(1538,310,'_elementor_css','a:4:{s:4:\"time\";i:1552617650;s:5:\"fonts\";a:0:{}s:6:\"status\";s:4:\"file\";i:0;s:0:\"\";}'),(1552,307,'_wp_page_template','default'),(1553,307,'_elementor_data','[{\"id\":\"2c80dfc\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"6a9f43a\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"a9d2d8d\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p>I designed a system that is used to keep track of chores in the house and the which user is supposed to do them.<\\/p><p>I used a PIC16f88 micro controller for this project. I programmed it in C using MPLAB X IDE.<\\/p><p>For interfacing, I used a 16x2 LCD for output and 4 debounced push buttons for input. I designed a custom PCB for the project and I\'m planning on making a 3-D printed enclosure for it.<\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"},{\"id\":\"d72d3a6\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p>the figures below shows the schematic and layout of the system.<\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"},{\"id\":\"cd176da\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/waseemorphali.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2019\\/12\\/Schematic.png\",\"id\":312},\"caption_source\":\"attachment\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"},{\"id\":\"154b76a\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/waseemorphali.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2019\\/12\\/Layout.png\",\"id\":313},\"caption_source\":\"attachment\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"},{\"id\":\"60a4c58\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p>I used the tools provided by easyeda.com to create the schematic and layout of the circuit.<\\/p><p>The circuit has 4 push buttons, but only two of them are used, the rest are left if I want to expand the functionality later on. They are wired and ready to be used, they only need to be programmed through the header pins on the left of the LCD.<\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"},{\"id\":\"5e714e0\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/waseemorphali.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2019\\/12\\/IMG_20191230_190339.jpg\",\"id\":314},\"caption_source\":\"attachment\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"},{\"id\":\"962e587\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/waseemorphali.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2019\\/12\\/IMG_20191230_190350.jpg\",\"id\":315},\"caption_source\":\"attachment\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false}]'),(1544,312,'_wp_attached_file','2019/12/Schematic.png'),(1545,312,'_wp_attachment_metadata','a:5:{s:5:\"width\";i:1165;s:6:\"height\";i:830;s:4:\"file\";s:21:\"2019/12/Schematic.png\";s:5:\"sizes\";a:10:{s:9:\"thumbnail\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:21:\"Schematic-150x150.png\";s:5:\"width\";i:150;s:6:\"height\";i:150;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:9:\"image/png\";}s:6:\"medium\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:21:\"Schematic-300x214.png\";s:5:\"width\";i:300;s:6:\"height\";i:214;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:9:\"image/png\";}s:12:\"medium_large\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:21:\"Schematic-768x547.png\";s:5:\"width\";i:768;s:6:\"height\";i:547;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:9:\"image/png\";}s:5:\"large\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:22:\"Schematic-1024x730.png\";s:5:\"width\";i:1024;s:6:\"height\";i:730;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:9:\"image/png\";}s:14:\"boxstyle-small\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:21:\"Schematic-200x200.png\";s:5:\"width\";i:200;s:6:\"height\";i:200;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:9:\"image/png\";}s:15:\"boxstyle-medium\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:21:\"Schematic-520x292.png\";s:5:\"width\";i:520;s:6:\"height\";i:292;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:9:\"image/png\";}s:14:\"boxstyle-large\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:21:\"Schematic-720x404.png\";s:5:\"width\";i:720;s:6:\"height\";i:404;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:9:\"image/png\";}s:13:\"boxstyle-list\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:21:\"Schematic-320x320.png\";s:5:\"width\";i:320;s:6:\"height\";i:320;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:9:\"image/png\";}s:9:\"alx-small\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:21:\"Schematic-200x200.png\";s:5:\"width\";i:200;s:6:\"height\";i:200;s:9:\"mime-type\";s:9:\"image/png\";}s:10:\"alx-medium\";a:4:{s:4:\"file\";s:21:\"Schematic-520x