,{\"id\":\"dca5edf\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"60fa5fe\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"0ae1cb6\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"spacer\"},{\"id\":\"d8d78a4\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"title\":\"<p id=\\\"Projects\\\">Projects<\\/p>\",\"title_color\":\"rgba(0,0,0,0.99)\",\"typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"typography_font_family\":\"Arial\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"heading\"},{\"id\":\"53c7b03\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"tabs\":[{\"tab_title\":\"Chores Tracker using PIC16f88 MCU\",\"tab_content\":\"<p>Nov 2019<\\/p><p><a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/waseemorphali.com\\/home-improvement-using-pic16f88-mcu\\/\\\">Click here<\\/a><\\/p><p>I created\\u00a0 a system to keep track of chores in the house using a PIC16f88 micro controller. I programmed the micro controller in C.<\\/p>\",\"_id\":\"b2a2830\"},{\"tab_title\":\"Implementation of Cyclic Redundancy Check on FPGA\",\"tab_content\":\"<p>Dec 2018<\\/p><p><a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/waseemorphali.com\\/implementation-of-cyclic-redundancy-check-on-fpga\\/\\\">Click here<\\/a><\\/p><p>I implemented three Cyclic Redundancy Check algorithms (CRC-8 , CRC-5 , CRC-3) on Intle\'s FPGA board DE2-70 using VHDL.<\\/p>\",\"_id\":\"f088114\"},{\"tab_title\":\"Implementation of Tree Pattern Matching\",\"tab_content\":\"<p>May 2018<\\/p><p><a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/waseemorphali.com\\/implementation-of-tree-pattern-matching\\/\\\">Click Here<\\/a><\\/p><p>We implemented an algorithm for tree pattern matching described in the IEEE paper \\\"A Parallel Algorithm and Architecture for Object Recognition in Images\\\".<\\/p><p>We used VHDL to implement the algorithm, and we added our own designed components to control data flow through the circuit.<\\/p>\",\"_id\":\"0de8aeb\"},{\"tab_title\":\"Design of a Wearable Augmented Reality System\",\"tab_content\":\"<p>May 2017<\\/p><p>Designed a simple augmented reality system using available components in the market.<\\/p>\",\"_id\":\"8e835f4\"},{\"tab_title\":\"Visually Servoed RC Toy Car\",\"tab_content\":\"<p>Dec 2015<\\/p><p><a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/waseemorphali.com\\/visually-servoed-rc-toy-car\\/\\\">Click Here<\\/a><\\/p><p>It was my capstone project for my undergraduate degree.\\u00a0We built a system that senses the position of a toy car and drives it automatically to the desired location through a PC.<\\/p>\",\"_id\":\"e0e4521\"},{\"tab_title\":\"Power System Design and Analysis\",\"tab_content\":\"<p>May 2015<\\/p><p><span class=\\\"fontstyle0\\\">Learned how to use ETAP software and designed a simple power network and analyzed it.<\\/span><\\/p>\",\"_id\":\"39efa38\"}]},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"accordion\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"2e1a31a\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"2b726ec\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"2114164\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"spacer\"},{\"id\":\"51284d3\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"title\":\"<p id=\\\"Skills\\\">Skills<\\/p>\",\"title_color\":\"rgba(0,0,0,0.99)\",\"typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"typography_font_family\":\"Arial\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"heading\"},{\"id\":\"6a52681\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":{\"structure\":\"20\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"2ded8ee\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":50,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"3327f42\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<ul><li><span class=\\\"fontstyle0\\\">Microsoft Office Suite<\\/span><\\/li><li><span class=\\\"fontstyle0\\\">C<\\/span><\\/li><li><span class=\\\"fontstyle0\\\">Python<\\/span><\\/li><li><span class=\\\"fontstyle0\\\">Matlab<\\/span><\\/li><li><span class=\\\"fontstyle0\\\">Assembly<\\/span><\\/li><li><span class=\\\"fontstyle0\\\">VHDL<\\/span><\\/li><\\/ul>\