150.png 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 225px) 100vw, 225px\" /></a></figure><h3><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/education/#Bsc\">Bsc. Electrical Engineering</a></h3><p>King Fahd University of Petroleum and Minerals</p>		\n			<figure><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/education/#Msc\"><img width=\"1272\" height=\"524\" src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Logo_of_New_Jersey_Institute_of_Technology.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Logo_of_New_Jersey_Institute_of_Technology.png 1272w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Logo_of_New_Jersey_Institute_of_Technology-300x124.png 300w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Logo_of_New_Jersey_Institute_of_Technology-768x316.png 768w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Logo_of_New_Jersey_Institute_of_Technology-1024x422.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1272px) 100vw, 1272px\" /></a></figure><h3><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/education/#Msc\">Msc. Electrical Engineering</a></h3><p>New Jersey Institute of Technology</p>		\n			<h2><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/experience/\">Experience</a></h2>		\n			<h2><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/experience/\">Senior Coach</a></h2>		\n			<h2><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/experience/#2\">Student Associate</a></h2>		\n			<h2><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/experience/#3\">Intern</a></h2>		\n		<p>                   Jan 2019 - Present</p><p>                   July 2018 - Dec 2018</p><p>                   June 2015 - Aug 2015</p>		\n			<h2><p id=\"Projects\">Projects</p></h2>		\n												<a href=\"\">Wi-Fi Enabled AC Thermostat</a>\n					<p>Nov 2019</p><p><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wi-fi-enabled-ac-thermostat/\">Click here</a></p><p>I built an interface for our old AC Thermostat so that it can be controlled using Wi-Fi.</p>\n												<a href=\"\">Chores Tracker using PIC16f88 MCU</a>\n					<p>Nov 2019</p><p><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/Chores-Tracker-using-pic16f88-mcu/\">Click here</a></p><p>I created  a system to keep track of chores in the house using a PIC16f88 micro controller. I programmed the micro controller in C.</p>\n												<a href=\"\">Implementation of Cyclic Redundancy Check on FPGA</a>\n					<p>Dec 2018</p><p><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/implementation-of-cyclic-redundancy-check-on-fpga/\">Click here</a></p><p>I implemented three Cyclic Redundancy Check algorithms (CRC-8 , CRC-5 , CRC-3) on Intle&#8217;s FPGA board DE2-70 using VHDL.</p>\n												<a href=\"\">Implementation of Tree Pattern Matching</a>\n					<p>May 2018</p><p><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/implementation-of-tree-pattern-matching/\">Click Here</a></p><p>We implemented an algorithm for tree pattern matching described in the IEEE paper &#8220;A Parallel Algorithm and Architecture for Object Recognition in Images&#8221;.</p><p>We used VHDL to implement the algorithm, and we added our own designed components to control data flow through the circuit.</p>\n												<a href=\"\">Design of a Wearable Augmented Reality System</a>\n					<p>May 2017</p><p>Designed a simple augmented reality system using available components in the market.</p>\n												<a href=\"\">Visually Servoed RC Toy Car</a>\n					<p>Dec 2015</p><p><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/visually-servoed-rc-toy-car/\">Click Here</a></p><p>It was my capstone project for my undergraduate degree. We built a system that senses the position of a toy car and drives it automatically to the desired location through a PC.</p>\n												<a href=\"\">Power System Design and Analysis</a>\n					<p>May 2015</p><p>Learned how to use ETAP software and designed a simple power network and analyzed it.</p>\n			<h2><p id=\"Skills\">Skills</p></h2>		\n		<ul><li>Microsoft Office Suite</li><li>C</li><li>Python</li><li>Matlab</li><li>Assembly</li><li>VHDL</li></ul><ul><li>Mentor Graphics</li><li>HSPICE</li><li>PLC Programming</li><li>Arduino</li><li>Fusion 360</li><li>Languages: English, Arabic, Spanish (elementary)</li></ul>','Home','','publish','closed','closed','','home','','','2019-12-31 01:33:06','2019-12-31 01:33:06','',0,'http://waseemorphali.com/?page_id=11',0,'page','',0),(9,1,'2018-12-01 00:02:47','2018-12-01 00:02:47','','WO','','inherit','open','closed','','wo','','','2018-12-01 00:02:47','2018-12-01 00:02:47','',0,'http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/WO.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(151,1,'2019-03-03 16:42:06','2019-03-03 16:42:06','<h2>Bsc. Electrical Engineering</h2>		\n		<p><strong>King Fahd University of Petroleum and Minerals</strong></p><p><strong>Jan 2011 - Dec 2015</strong></p><p><strong>GPA: 3.12 / 4</strong></p><p><strong>High Level Courses:</strong></p><ul><li><strong>PLC Programming:</strong> Learned programming Siemens PLCs using ladder programming.</li><li><strong>Process Control: </strong>PID controllers and linear systems.</li><li><strong>Power System Analysis: </strong>Used ETAP software to design and analyse power system.</li><li><strong>Telecommunication Networks</strong></li><li><strong>Analogue Communication Electronics</strong></li></ul>		\n											<a href=\"www.kfupm.edu.sa/\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"\" target=\"_blank\">\n							<img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/download-150x150.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/download-150x150.png 150w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/download.png 225w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" />								</a>\n			<h2>Msc. Electrical Engneering</h2>		\n		<p><strong>New Jersey Institute of Technology</strong></p><p><strong>Jan 2017 - Dec 2018</strong></p><p><strong>GPA: 3.9 / 4</strong></p><p><strong>Key Courses:</strong></p><ul><li><strong>VLSI Design 1: </strong>Used Mentor Graphics tools and PSPICE to design and simulate schematics and layouts.</li><li><strong>VLSI Design 2: </strong>Learned VHDL and used it to implement a pattern matching algorithm taken from a research paper.</li><li><strong>Digital Signal Processing: </strong>Learned DSP and used VHDL to design and implement a CRC generator circuit on Intel DE2_70 board. </li><li><strong>Computer System Architecture</strong></li><li><strong>Computer Arithmetic Algorithms</strong></li></ul>		\n											<a href=\"www.njit.edu/\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"\" target=\"_blank\">\n							<img width=\"620\" height=\"256\" src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Logo_of_New_Jersey_Institute_of_Technology-1024x422.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Logo_of_New_Jersey_Institute_of_Technology-1024x422.png 1024w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Logo_of_New_Jersey_Institute_of_Technology-300x124.png 300w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Logo_of_New_Jersey_Institute_of_Technology-768x316.png 768w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Logo_of_New_Jersey_Institute_of_Technology.png 1272w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" />								</a>','Education','','inherit','closed','closed','','117-revision-v1','','','2019-03-03 16:42:06','2019-03-03 16:42:06','',117,'http://waseemorphali.com/117-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(116,1,'2019-01-29 20:54:01','2019-01-29 20:54:01','http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/cropped-waseem-bw.png','cropped-waseem-bw.png','','inherit','open','closed','','cropped-waseem-bw-png','','','2019-01-29 20:54:01','2019-01-29 20:54:01','',0,'http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/cropped-waseem-bw.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(150,1,'2019-03-03 16:40:43','2019-03-03 16:40:43','<h2>Bsc. Electrical Engineering</h2>		\n		<p><strong>King Fahd University of Petroleum and Minerals</strong></p><p><strong>Jan 2011 - Dec 2015</strong></p><p><strong>GPA: 3.12 / 4</strong></p><p><strong>High Level Courses:</strong></p><ul><li><strong>PLC Programming:</strong> Learned programming Siemens PLCs using ladder programming.</li><li><strong>Process Control: </strong>PID controllers and linear systems.</li><li><strong>Analogue Communication Electronics</strong></li><li><strong>Power System Analysis: </strong>Used ETAP software to design and analyse power system.</li><li><strong>Telecommunication Networks</strong></li></ul>		\n											<a href=\"www.kfupm.edu.sa/\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"\" target=\"_blank\">\n							<img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/download-150x150.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/download-150x150.png 150w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/download.png 225w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" />								</a>\n			<h2>Msc. Electrical Engneering</h2>		\n		<p><strong>New Jersey Institute of Technology</strong></p><p><strong>Jan 2017 - Dec 2018</strong></p><p><strong>GPA: 3.9 / 4</strong></p><p><strong>Key Courses:</strong></p><ul><li><strong>VLSI Design 1: </strong>Used Mentor Graphics tools and PSPICE to design and simulate schematics and layouts.</li><li><strong>VLSI Design 2: </strong>Learned VHDL and used it to implement a pattern matching algorithm taken from a research paper.</li><li><strong>Computer System Architecture</strong></li><li><strong>Computer Arithmetic Algorithms</strong></li><li><strong>Digital Signal Processing: </strong>Learned DSP and used VHDL to design and implement a CRC generator circuit on Intel DE2_70 board. </li></ul>		\n											<a href=\"www.njit.edu/\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"\" target=\"_blank\">\n							<img width=\"620\" height=\"256\" src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Logo_of_New_Jersey_Institute_of_Technology-1024x422.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Logo_of_New_Jersey_Institute_of_Technology-1024x422.png 1024w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Logo_of_New_Jersey_Institute_of_Technology-300x124.png 300w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Logo_of_New_Jersey_Institute_of_Technology-768x316.png 768w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Logo_of_New_Jersey_Institute_of_Technology.png 1272w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" />								</a>','Education','','inherit','closed','closed','','117-revision-v1','','','2019-03-03 16:40:43','2019-03-03 16:40:43','',117,'http://waseemorphali.com/117-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(29,1,'2018-12-01 00:50:59','2018-12-01 00:50:59','','study_cover.jpg','','inherit','open','closed','','study_cover-jpg','','','2018-12-01 00:50:59','2018-12-01 00:50:59','',0,'http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/study_cover.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(30,1,'2018-12-01 00:51:00','2018-12-01 00:51:00','','study_1.jpg','','inherit','open','closed','','study_1-jpg','','','2018-12-01 00:51:00','2018-12-01 00:51:00','',0,'http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/study_1.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(31,1,'2018-12-01 00:51:00','2018-12-01 00:51:00','','teacther1.png','','inherit','open','closed','','teacther1-png','','','2018-12-01 00:51:00','2018-12-01 00:51:00','',0,'http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/teacther1.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(32,1,'2018-12-01 00:51:01','2018-12-01 00:51:01','','teacher2.jpg','','inherit','open','closed','','teacher2-jpg','','','2018-12-01 00:51:01','2018-12-01 00:51:01','',0,'http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/teacher2.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(33,1,'2018-12-01 00:51:01','2018-12-01 00:51:01','','teacher3.jpg','','inherit','open','closed','','teacher3-jpg','','','2018-12-01 00:51:01','2018-12-01 00:51:01','',0,'http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/teacher3.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(34,1,'2018-12-01 00:51:01','2018-12-01 00:51:01','','study-box_1.jpg','','inherit','open','closed','','study-box_1-jpg','','','2018-12-01 0