morphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/20190302_111425-e1552241714119.jpg\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"93af0a1\" data-elementor-lightbox-index=\"2\"><img src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/20190302_111425-320x320.jpg\" alt=\"20190302_111425\" /></a></figure><figure><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/IMG_7862.jpg\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"93af0a1\" data-elementor-lightbox-index=\"3\"><img src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/IMG_7862-320x320.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_7862\" /></a></figure>			\n		<ul><li>I coached students enrolled in the program on coding in Python, Arduino, 3-D modeling and printing and tech.</li><li>I supervised and trained 3 junior coaches.</li><li>I mentored a group of high school students building a robot to compete in FIRST Robotics Competition (FRC) 2019.</li><li>Shown in the pictures is the team of students I coached for FRC 2019.</li><li>Also shown is the robot that we built for the competition.</li></ul>		\n			<h2><p id=\"2\">Student Associate</p></h2>		\n		<p><strong>NJIT Strategic Events and Conference Services, Newark, NJ</strong></p><p>July 2018 - Dec 2018</p>		\n				<figure><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/4.jpeg\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"73b26ac\" data-elementor-lightbox-index=\"0\"><img src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/4-320x320.jpeg\" alt=\"4\" /></a></figure><figure><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/1.jpeg\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"73b26ac\" data-elementor-lightbox-index=\"1\"><img src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/1-320x320.jpeg\" alt=\"1\" /></a></figure><figure><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/3.jpeg\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"73b26ac\" data-elementor-lightbox-index=\"2\"><img src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/3-320x320.jpeg\" alt=\"3\" /></a></figure><figure><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/2-e1552263604927.jpeg\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"73b26ac\" data-elementor-lightbox-index=\"3\"><img src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/2-e1552263604927-320x320.jpeg\" alt=\"2\" /></a></figure><figure><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/5.jpeg\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"73b26ac\" data-elementor-lightbox-index=\"4\"><img src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/5-320x320.jpeg\" alt=\"5\" /></a></figure>			\n		<ul><li>I was an information desk attendant helping people in the campus center .</li><li>I worked as an usher in events around NJIT where my responsibilities included helping out in organizing, setting up and greeting guests attending the events.</li></ul>		\n			<h2><p id=\"3\">Intern</p></h2>		\n		<p><strong>Grundfos Gulf Distribution, Dubai, UAE</strong></p><p>June 2015 - Aug 2015</p>		\n				<figure><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/20150730_095112-e1552265017540.jpg\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"977d15a\" data-elementor-lightbox-index=\"0\"><img src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/20150730_095112-320x320.jpg\" alt=\"20150730_095112\" /></a></figure><figure><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/20150614_141040-e1552265732695.jpg\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"977d15a\" data-elementor-lightbox-index=\"1\"><img src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/20150614_141040-e1552265149822-320x320.jpg\" alt=\"20150614_141040\" /></a></figure><figure><a h