16.png 768w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Logo_of_New_Jersey_Institute_of_Technology.png 1272w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" />								</a>\n			<h2><p id=\"Bsc\">Bsc. Electrical Engineering</p></h2>		\n		<p><strong>King Fahd University of Petroleum and Minerals</strong></p><p><strong>Jan 2011 - Dec 2015</strong></p><p><strong>GPA: 3.12 / 4</strong></p><p><strong>High Level Courses:</strong></p><ul><li><strong>PLC Programming:</strong> Learned programming Siemens PLCs using ladder programming.</li><li><strong>Process Control: </strong>PID controllers and linear systems.</li><li><strong>Power System Analysis: </strong>Used ETAP software to design and analyse power system.</li><li><strong>Telecommunication Networks</strong></li><li><strong>Analogue Communication Electronics</strong></li></ul>		\n											<a href=\"www.kfupm.edu.sa/\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"\" target=\"_blank\">\n							<img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/download-150x150.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/download-150x150.png 150w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/download.png 225w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" />								</a>','Education','','publish','closed','closed','','education','','','2019-12-30 23:48:07','2019-12-30 23:48:07','',0,'http://waseemorphali.com/?page_id=117',0,'page','',0),(101,1,'2019-01-29 17:07:38','2019-01-29 17:07:38','<h1>Waseem Orphali</h1>		\n			<h4>Electrical Enginner</h4>		\n										<img width=\"200\" height=\"200\" src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/waseem-bw.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/waseem-bw.png 200w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/waseem-bw-150x150.png 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px\" />											\n			<h3>Experience</h3>		\n			<h5>Jan 2019 - Present</h5>		\n			<h3>Robotics Coach</h3>	