imulation-1024x182.jpg 1024w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/crc1-simulation-300x53.jpg 300w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/crc1-simulation-768x137.jpg 768w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/crc1-simulation.jpg 1100w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" />											<figcaption>crc1 shows the CRC-5 code to be attached</figcaption>\n										</figure>\n							<figure>\n										<img width=\"620\" height=\"112\" src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/crc2-simulation-1024x185.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/crc2-simulation-1024x185.jpg 1024w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/crc2-simulation-300x54.jpg 300w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/crc2-simulation-768x139.jpg 768w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/crc2-simulation.jpg 1082w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" />											<figcaption>crc1 shows the CRC-8 code to be attached</figcaption>\n										</figure>\n										<img width=\"620\" height=\"349\" src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/20181217_115414-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/20181217_115414-1024x576.jpg 1024w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/20181217_115414-300x169.jpg 300w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/20181217_115414-768x432.jpg 768w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/20181217_115414-520x292.jpg 520w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/20181217_115414-720x404.jpg 720w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" />','Implementation of Cyclic Redundancy Check on FPGA','','inherit','closed','closed','','209-revision-v1','','','2019-03-14 18:28:28','2019-03-14 18:28:28','',209,'http://waseemorphali.com/209-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(220,1,'2019-03-14 17:34:41','2019-03-14 17:34:41','','20181217_115414',