2019/03/crc1-simulation-300x53.jpg 300w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/crc1-simulation-768x137.jpg 768w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/crc1-simulation.jpg 1100w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" />											<figcaption>crc1 shows the CRC-5 code to be attached</figcaption>\n										</figure>\n							<figure>\n										<img width=\"620\" height=\"112\" src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/crc2-simulation-1024x185.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/crc2-simulation-1024x185.jpg 1024w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/crc2-simulation-300x54.jpg 300w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/crc2-simulation-768x139.jpg 768w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/crc2-simulation.jpg 1082w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" />											<figcaption>crc2 shows the CRC-8 code to be attached</figcaption>\n										</figure>\n		<p>I presented the circuit and code to the professor and demonstrated the how the code works on the DE2-70 board</p>		\n										<img width=\"620\" height=\"349\" src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/20181217_115414-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/20181217_115414-1024x576.jpg 1024w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/20181217_115414-300x169.jpg 300w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/20181217_115414-768x432.jpg 768w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/20181217_115414-520x292.jpg 520w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/20181217_115414-720x404.jpg 720w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" />','Implementation of Cyclic Redundancy Check on FPGA','','inherit','closed','closed','','209-revision-v1','','','2019-03-14 18:31:32','2019-03-14 18:31:32','',209,'http://waseemorphali.com/209-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(227,1,'2019-03-14 18:32:30','2019-03-14 18:32:30','','Implementation of Tree Pattern Matching','','inherit','closed','closed','','211-revision-v1','','','2019-03-14 18:32:30','2019-03-14 18:32:30','',211,'http://waseemorphali.com/211-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(229,1,'2019-03-14 22:11:19','2019-03-14 22:11:19','<p>We implemented an algorithm for tree pattern matching described in the IEEE paper \"<a href=\"https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/document/1598158\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">A Parallel Algorithm and Architecture for Object Recognition in Images</a>\".<br />We used VHDL to implement the algorithm, and we added our own designed components to control data flow through the circuit.</p>','Implementation of Tree Pattern Matching','','inherit','closed','closed','','211-revision-v1','','','2019-03-14 22:11:19','2019-03-14 22:11:19','',211,'http://waseemorphali.com/211-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(231,1,'2019-03-14 22:37:08','2019-03-14 22:37:08','','complete diagram','','inherit','open','closed','','complete-diagram','','','2019-03-14 22:37:08','2019-03-14 22:37:08','',211,'http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/complete-diagram.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(232,1,'2019-03-14 22:40:31','2019-03-14 22:40:31','<p>We implemented an algorithm for tree pattern matching described in the IEEE paper \"<a href=\"https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/document/1598158\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">A Parallel Algorithm and Architecture for Object Recognition in Images</a>\".<br />We used VHDL to implement the algorithm, and we added our own designed components to control data flow through the circuit. The team consisted of 4 students, I was the leader of the group.</p>		\n							<figure>\n										<img width=\"620\" height=\"434\" src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/complete-diagram.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/complete-diagram.png 816w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/complete-diagram-300x210.png 300w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/complete-diagram-768x537.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" />											<figcaption>System block diagram</figcaption>\n										</figure>\n		<p>The system proposed in the paper uses processing elements (PEs) to process the data serially and send the result back, we designed and added memory blocks that handle data input and a controller to handle data distribution and control of the different PEs and registers.</p>','Implementation of Tree Pattern Matching','','inherit','closed','closed','','211-revision-v1','','','2019-03-14 22:40:31','2019-03-14 22:40:31','',211,'http://waseemorphali.com/211-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(233,1,'2019-03-14 22:41:57','2019-03-14 22:41:57','','top part diagram','','inherit','open','closed','','top-part-diagram','','','2019-03-14 22:41:57','2019-03-14 22:41:57','',211,'http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/top-part-diagram.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(234,1,'2019-03-14 22:42:27','2019-03-14 22:42:27','','bottom part diagram','','inherit','open','closed','','bottom-part-diagram','','','2019-03-14 22:42:27','2019-03-14 22:42:27','',211,'http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/bottom-part-diagram.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(235,1,'2019-03-14 22:43:10','2019-03-14 22:43:10','<p>We implemented an algorithm for tree pattern matching described in the IEEE paper \"<a href=\"https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/document/1598158\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">A Parallel Algorithm and Architecture for Object Recognition in Images</a>\".<br />We used VHDL to implement the algorithm, and we added our own designed components to control data flow through the circuit. The team consisted of 4 students, I was the leader of the group.</p>		\n							<figure>\n										<img width=\"620\" height=\"434\" src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/complete-diagram.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/complete-diagram.png 816w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/complete-diagram-300x210.png 300w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/complete-diagram-768x537.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" />											<figcaption>System block diagram</figcaption>\n										</figure>\n		<p>The system proposed in the paper uses processing elements (PEs) to process the data serially and send the result back, we designed and added memory blocks that handle data input and a controller to handle data distribution and control of the different PEs and registers. The detailed diagrams of the top and bottom parts of the system are shown below.</p>		\n							<figure>\n										<img width=\"620\" height=\"337\" src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/top-part-diagram.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/top-part-diagram.png 678w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/top-part-diagram-300x163.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" />											<figcaption>Top part</figcaption>\n										</figure>\n							<figure>\n										<img width=\"493\" height=\"456\" src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/bottom-part-diagram.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/bottom-part-diagram.png 493w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/bottom-part-diagram-300x277.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 493px) 100vw, 493px\" />											<figcaption>Bottom part</figcaption>\n										</figure>','Implementation of Tree Pattern Matching','','inherit','closed','closed','','211-revision-v1','','','2019-03-14 22:43:10','2019-03-14 22:43:10','',211,'http://waseemorphali.com/211-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(236,1,'2019-03-14 22:47:01','2019-03-14 22:47:01','','State Diagram','','inherit','open','closed','','state-diagram','','','2019-03-14 22:47:01','2019-03-14 22:47:01','',211,'http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/State-Diagram.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(238,1,'2019-03-14 22:48:13','2019-03-14 22:48:13','<p>We implemented an algorithm for tree pattern matching described in the IEEE paper \"<a href=\"https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/document/1598158\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">A Parallel Algorithm and Architecture for Object Recognition in Images</a>\".<br />We used VHDL to implement the algorithm, and we added our own designed components to control data flow through the circuit. The team consisted of 4 students, I was the leader of the group.</p>		\n							<figure>\n										<img width=\"620\" height=\"434\" src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/complete-diagram.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/complete-diagram.png 816w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/complete-diagram-300x210.png 300w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/complete-diagram-768x537.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" />											<figcaption>System block diagram</figcaption>\n										</figure>\n		<p>The system proposed in the paper uses processing elements (PEs) to process the data serially and send the result back, we designed and added memory blocks that handle data input and a controller to handle data distribution and control of the different PEs and registers. The detailed diagrams of the top and bottom parts of the system are shown below.</p>		\n							<figure>\n										<img width=\"620\" height=\"337\" src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/top-part-diagram.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/top-part-diagram.png 678w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/top-part-diagram-300x163.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" />											<figcaption>Top part</figcaption>\n										</figure>\n							<figure>\n										<img width=\"493\" height=\"456\" src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/bottom-part-diagram.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/bottom-part-diagram.png 493w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/bottom-part-diagram-300x277.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 493px) 100vw, 493px\" />											<figcaption>Bottom part</figcaption>\n										</figure>\n		<p>The controller is built using a state machine whose diagram is shown below. </p>		\n										<img width=\"620\" height=\"484\" src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/State-Diagram.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/State-Diagram.png 701w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/State-Diagram-300x234.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" />','Implementation of Tree Pattern Matching','','inherit','closed','closed','','211-revision-v1','','','2019-03-14 22:48:13','2019-03-14 22:48:13','',211,'http://waseemorphali.com/211-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(237,1,'2019-03-14 22:47:44','2019-03-14 22:47:44','<p>We implemented an algorithm for tree pattern matching described in the IEEE paper \"<a href=\"https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/document/1598158\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">A Parallel Algorithm and Architecture for Object Recognition in Images</a>\".<br />We used VHDL to implement the algorithm, and we added our own designed components to control data flow through the circuit. The team consisted of 4 students, I was the leader of the group.</p>		\n							<figure>\n											<a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/complete-diagram.png\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\">\n							<img width=\"620\" height=\"434\" src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/complete-diagram.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/complete-diagram.png 816w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/complete-diagram-300x210.png 300w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/complete-diagram-768x537.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" />								</a>\n											<figcaption>System block diagram</figcaption>\n										</figure>\n		<p>The system proposed in the paper uses processing elements (PEs) to process the data serially and send the result back, we designed and added memory blocks that handle data input and a controller to handle data distribution and control of the different PEs and registers. The detailed diagrams of the top and bottom parts of the system are shown below.</p>		\n							<figure>\n										<img width=\"620\" height=\"337\" src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/top-part-diagram.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/top-part-diagram.png 678w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/top-part-diagram-300x163.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" />											<figcaption>Top part</figcaption>\n										</figure>\n							<figure>\n										<img width=\"493\" height=\"456\" src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/bottom-part-diagram.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/bottom-part-diagram.png 493w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/bottom-part-diagram-300x277.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 493px) 100vw, 493px\" />											<figcaption>Bottom part</figcaption>\n										</figure>\n		<p>The controller is built using a state machine whose diagram is shown below. </p>		\n										<img width=\"620\" height=\"484\" src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/State-Diagram.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/State-Diagram.png 701w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/State-Diagram-300x234.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" />','Implementation of Tree Pattern Matching','','inherit','closed','closed','','211-revision-v1','','','2019-03-14 22:47:44','2019-03-14 22:47:44','',211,'http://waseemorphali.com/211-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(239,1,'2019-03-14 22:51:58','2019-03-14 22:51:58','<p>We implemented an algorithm for tree pattern matching described in the IEEE paper \"<a href=\"https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/document/1598158\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">A Parallel Algorithm and Architecture for Object Recognition in Images</a>\".<br />We used VHDL to implement the algorithm, and we added our own designed components to control data flow through the circuit. The team consisted of 4 students, I was the leader of the group.</p><p>We used ModelSim to simulate and test the VHDL code.</p>		\n							<figure>\n										<img width=\"620\" height=\"434\" src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/complete-diagram.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/complete-diagram.png 816w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/complete-diagram-300x210.png 300w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/complete-diagram-768x537.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" />											<figcaption>System block diagram</figcaption>\n										</figure>\n		<p>The system proposed in the paper uses processing elements (PEs) to process the data serially and send the result back, we designed and added memory blocks that handle data input and a controller to handle data distribution and control of the different PEs and registers. The detailed diagrams of the top and bottom parts of the system are shown below.</p>		\n							<figure>\n										<img width=\"620\" height=\"337\" src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/top-part-diagram.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/top-part-diagram.png 678w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/top-part-diagram-300x163.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" />											<figcaption>Top part</figcaption>\n										</figure>\n							<figure>\n										<img width=\"493\" height=\"456\" src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/bottom-part-diagram.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/bottom-part-diagram.png 493w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/bottom-part-diagram-300x277.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 493px) 100vw, 493px\" />											<figcaption>Bottom part</figcaption>\n										</figure>\n		<p>The controller is built using a state machine whose diagram is shown below.</p>		\n										<img width=\"620\" height=\"484\" src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/State-Diagram.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/State-Diagram.png 701w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/State-Diagram-300x234.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" />','Implementation of Tree Pattern Matching','','inherit','closed','closed','','211-revision-v1','','','2019-03-14 22:51:58','2019-03-14 22:51:58','',211,'http://waseemorphali.com/211-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(240,1,'2019-03-14 22:54:35','2019-03-14 22:54:35','','20180508_210023','','inherit','open','closed','','20180508_210023','','','2019-03-14 22:54:35','2019-03-14 22:54:35','',211,'http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/20180508_210023.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(243,1,'2019-03-14 22:58:11','2019-03-14 22:58:11','<p>We implemented an algorithm for tree pattern matching described in the IEEE paper \"<a href=\"https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/document/1598158\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">A Parallel Algorithm and Architecture for Object Recognition in Images</a>\".<br />We used VHDL to implement the algorithm, and we added our own designed components to control data flow through the circuit. The team consisted of 4 students, I was the leader of the group.</p><p>We used ModelSim to simulate and test the VHDL code.</p>		\n							<figure>\n										<img width=\"620\" height=\"434\" src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/complete-diagram.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/complete-diagram.png 816w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/complete-diagram-300x210.png 300w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/complete-diagram-768x537.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" />											<figcaption>System block diagram</figcaption>\n										</figure>\n		<p>The system proposed in the paper uses processing elements (PEs) to process the data serially and send the result back, we designed and added memory blocks that handle data input and a controller to handle data distribution and control of the different PEs and registers. The detailed diagrams of the top and bottom parts of the system are shown below.</p>		\n							<figure>\n										<img width=\"620\" height=\"337\" src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/top-part-diagram.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/top-part-diagram.png 678w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/top-part-diagram-300x163.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" />											<figcaption>Top part</figcaption>\n										</figure>\n							<figure>\n										<img width=\"493\" height=\"456\" src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/bottom-part-diagram.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/bottom-part-diagram.png 493w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/bottom-part-diagram-300x277.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 493px) 100vw, 493px\" />											<figcaption>Bottom part</figcaption>\n										</figure>\n		<p>The controller is built using a state machine whose diagram is shown below.</p>		\n										<img width=\"620\" height=\"484\" src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/State-Diagram.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/State-Diagram.png 701w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/State-Diagram-300x234.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" />											\n		<p>In the end, I gained very good experience in VHDL, and in working as part of a team on a challenging project.</p>		\n										<img width=\"620\" height=\"465\" src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/20180508_210023-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/20180508_210023-1024x768.jpg 1024w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/20180508_210023-300x225.jpg 300w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/20180508_210023-768x576.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" />','Projects','','inherit','closed','closed','','211-revision-v1','','','2019-03-14 22:58:11','2019-03-14 22:58:11','',211,'http://waseemorphali.com/211-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(242,1,'2019-03-14 22:58:11','2019-03-14 22:58:11','<p>We implemented an algorithm for tree pattern matching described in the IEEE paper \"<a href=\"https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/document/1598158\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">A Parallel Algorithm and Architecture for Object Recognition in Images</a>\".<br />We used VHDL to implement the algorithm, and we added our own designed components to control data flow through the circuit. The team consisted of 4 students, I was the leader of the group.</p><p>We used ModelSim to simulate and test the VHDL code.</p>		\n							<figure>\n										<img width=\"620\" height=\"434\" src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/complete-diagram.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/complete-diagram.png 816w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/complete-diagram-300x210.png 300w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/complete-diagram-768x537.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" />											<figcaption>System block diagram</figcaption>\n										</figure>\n		<p>The system proposed in the paper uses processing elements (PEs) to process the data serially and send the result back, we designed and added memory blocks that handle data input and a controller to handle data distribution and control of the different PEs and registers. The detailed diagrams of the top and bottom parts of the system are shown below.</p>		\n							<figure>\n										<img width=\"620\" height=\"337\" src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/top-part-diagram.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/top-part-diagram.png 678w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/top-part-diagram-300x163.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" />											<figcaption>Top part</figcaption>\n										</figure>\n							<figure>\n										<img width=\"493\" height=\"456\" src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/bottom-part-diagram.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/bottom-part-diagram.png 493w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/bottom-part-diagram-300x277.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 493px) 100vw, 493px\" />											<figcaption>Bottom part</figcaption>\n										</figure>\n		<p>The controller is built using a state machine whose diagram is shown below.</p>		\n										<img width=\"620\" height=\"484\" src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/State-Diagram.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/State-Diagram.png 701w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/State-Diagram-300x234.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" />','Projects','','inherit','closed','closed','','211-revision-v1','','','2019-03-14 22:58:11','2019-03-14 22:58:11','',211,'http://waseemorphali.com/211-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(244,1,'2019-03-14 22:58:27','2019-03-14 22:58:27','<p>We implemented an algorithm for tree pattern matching described in the IEEE paper \"<a href=\"https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/document/1598158\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">A Parallel Algorithm and Architecture for Object Recognition in Images</a>\".<br />We used VHDL to implement the algorithm, and we added our own designed components to control data flow through the circuit. The team consisted of 4 students, I was the leader of the group.</p><p>We used ModelSim to simulate and test the VHDL code.</p>		\n							<figure>\n										<img width=\"620\" height=\"434\" src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/complete-diagram.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/complete-diagram.png 816w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/complete-diagram-300x210.png 300w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/complete-diagram-768x537.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" />											<figcaption>System block diagram</figcaption>\n										</figure>\n		<p>The system proposed in the paper uses processing elements (PEs) to process the data serially and send the result back, we designed and added memory blocks that handle data input and a controller to handle data distribution and control of the different PEs and registers. The detailed diagrams of the top and bottom parts of the system are shown below.</p>		\n							<figure>\n										<img width=\"620\" height=\"337\" src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/top-part-diagram.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/top-part-diagram.png 678w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/top-part-diagram-300x163.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" />											<figcaption>Top part</figcaption>\n										</figure>\n							<figure>\n										<img width=\"493\" height=\"456\" src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/bottom-part-diagram.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/bottom-part-diagram.png 493w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/bottom-part-diagram-300x277.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 493px) 100vw, 493px\" />											<figcaption>Bottom part</figcaption>\n										</figure>\n		<p>The controller is built using a state machine whose diagram is shown below.</p>		\n										<img width=\"620\" height=\"484\" src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/State-Diagram.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/State-Diagram.png 701w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/State-Diagram-300x234.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" />											\n		<p>In the end, I gained very good experience in VHDL, and in working as part of a team on a challenging project.</p>		\n										<img width=\"620\" height=\"465\" src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/20180508_210023-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/20180508_210023-1024x768.jpg 1024w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/20180508_210023-300x225.jpg 300w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/20180508_210023-768x576.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" />','Implementation of Tree Pattern Matching','','inherit','closed','closed','','211-revision-v1','','','2019-03-14 22:58:27','2019-03-14 22:58:27','',211,'http://waseemorphali.com/211-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(310,1,'2019-12-30 23:53:40','2019-12-30 23:53:40','We implemented an algorithm for tree pattern matching described in the IEEE paper \"<a href=\"https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/document/1598158\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">A Parallel Algorithm and Architecture for Object Recognition in Images</a>\".\nWe used VHDL to implement the algorithm, and we added our own designed components to control data flow through th