Diagram.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/State-Diagram.png 701w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/State-Diagram-300x234.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\">\n\nIn the end, we delivered a good system inspired by the paper and designed by us. Also, I gained very good experience in VHDL, and in working as part of a team on a challenging project.\n\n<img width=\"620\" height=\"465\" src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/20180508_210023-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/20180508_210023-1024x768.jpg 1024w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/20180508_210023-300x225.jpg 300w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/20180508_210023-768x576.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\">','Implementation of Tree Pattern Matching','','inherit','closed','closed','','211-revision-v1','','','2019-12-30 23:53:40','2019-12-30 23:53:40','',211,'http://waseemorphali.com/211-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(246,1,'2019-03-14 23:01:45','2019-03-14 23:01:45','<p>We implemented an algorithm for tree pattern matching described in the IEEE paper \"<a href=\"https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/document/1598158\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">A Parallel Algorithm and Architecture for Object Recognition in Images</a>\".<br />We used VHDL to implement the algorithm, and we added our own designed components to control data flow through the circuit. The team consisted of 4 students, I was the leader of the group.</p><p>We used ModelSim to simulate and test the VHDL code.</p>		\n							<figure>\n										<img width=\"620\" height=\"434\" src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/complete-diagram.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/complete-diagram.png 816w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/complete-diagram-300x210.png 300w, http://waseemorpha