d experience in VHDL, and in working as part of a team on a challenging project.</p>		\n										<img width=\"620\" height=\"465\" src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/20180508_210023-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/20180508_210023-1024x768.jpg 1024w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/20180508_210023-300x225.jpg 300w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/20180508_210023-768x576.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" />','Implementation of Tree Pattern Matching','','inherit','closed','closed','','211-revision-v1','','','2019-03-14 23:01:45','2019-03-14 23:01:45','',211,'http://waseemorphali.com/211-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(247,1,'2019-03-14 23:45:40','2019-03-14 23:45:40','<p>We built a system that senses the position of a toy car and drives it automatically to the desired location through a PC.</p>','Visually Servoed RC Toy Car','','inherit','closed','closed','','213-revision-v1','','','2019-03-14 23:45:40','2019-03-14 23:45:40','',213,'http://waseemorphali.com/213-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(253,1,'2019-03-15 01:54:16','2019-03-15 01:54:16','<p>We built a system that sees the position of a toy car using a camera fixed to the ceiling and drives it automatically to the desired location.</p><p>We coded the system in MATLAB. We used image processing to identify the car\'s position and destination and we coded 3 different methods of control to guide the car to the destination.</p>		\n				<figure><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Car.png\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"1fe0c25\" data-elementor-lightbox-index=\"0\"><img src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Car.png\" alt=\"Car\" /></a><figcaption>Car</figcaption></figure><figure><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/car2.png\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"1fe0c25\" data-elementor-lightbox-index=\"1\"><img src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/car2.png\" alt=\"Subtracted Background\" /></a><figcaption>Subtracted Background</figcaption></figure><figure><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/car3.png\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"1fe0c25\" data-elementor-lightbox-index=\"2\"><img src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/car3.png\" alt=\"Gaussian Filter\" /></a><figcaption>Gaussian Filter</figcaption></figure><figure><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/car4.png\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"1fe0c25\" data-elementor-lightbox-index=\"3\"><img src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/car4.png\" alt=\"Threshold Applied\" /></a><figcaption>Threshold Applied</figcaption></figure>','Visually Servoed RC Toy Car','','inherit','closed','closed','','213-revision-v1','','','2019-03-15 01:54:16','2019-03-15 01:54:16','',213,'http://waseemorphali.com/213-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(249,1,'2019-03-15 01:50:52','2019-03-15 01:50:52','','Car','Car','inherit','open','closed','','car','','','2019-03-15 01:52:53','2019-03-15 01:52:53','',213,'http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Car.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(250,1,'2019-03-15 01:51:01','2019-03-15 01:51:01','','car2','Subtracted Background','inherit','open','closed','','car2','','','2019-03-15 01:53:26','2019-03-15 01:53:26','',213,'http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/car2.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(251,1,'2019-03-15 01:51:06','2019-03-15 01:51:06','','car3','Gaussian Filter','inherit','open','closed','','car3','','','2019-03-15 01:53:32','2019-03-15 01:53:32','',213,'http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/car3.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(252,1,'2019-03-15 01:51:09','2019-03-15 01:51:09','','car4','Threshold Applied','inherit','open','closed','','car4','','','2019-03-15 01:53:41','2019-03-15 01:53:41','',213,'http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/car4.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(254,1,'2019-03-15 02:00:45','2019-03-15 02:00:45','','Car','','inherit','open','closed','','car-2','','','2019-03-15 02:00:45','2019-03-15 02:00:45','',213,'http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Car.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(255,1,'2019-03-15 02:01:15','2019-03-15 02:01:15','<p>We built a system that sees the position of a toy car using a camera fixed to the ceiling and drives it automatically to the desired location.</p><p>We coded the system in MATLAB. We used image processing to identify the car\'s position and destination and we coded 3 different methods of control to guide the car to the destination.</p><p>The image processing technique we used was background subtraction. This method easily detects the car since it\'s the only object moving in the environment. A Gaussian filter was applied to reduce the noise after subtraction and then a threshold was applied and the remaining pixel locations was averaged to get the car\'s location. The process is shown below.</p>		\n				<figure><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Car.png\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"1fe0c25\" data-elementor-lightbox-index=\"0\"><img src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Car.png\" alt=\"Car\" /></a><figcaption>Car</figcaption></figure><figure><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/car2.png\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"1fe0c25\" data-elementor-lightbox-index=\"1\"><img src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/car2.png\" alt=\"Subtracted Background\" /></a><figcaption>Subtracted Background</figcaption></figure><figure><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/car3.png\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"1fe0c25\" data-elementor-lightbox-index=\"2\"><img src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/car3.png\" alt=\"Gaussian Filter\" /></a><figcaption>Gaussian Filter</figcaption></figure><figure><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/car4.png\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"1fe0c25\" data-elementor-lightbox-index=\"3\"><img src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/car4.png\" alt=\"Threshold Applied\" /></a><figcaption>Threshold Applied</figcaption></figure>			\n		<p>We used a cheap remote controlled toy car we bought from the local market and we modified its motor because it was too fast to be controlled accurately.</p>		\n										<img width=\"300\" height=\"225\" src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Car-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Car-300x225.jpg 300w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Car-768x576.jpg 768w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Car-1024x768.jpg 1024w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Car.jpg 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" />','Visually Servoed RC Toy Car','','inherit','closed','closed','','213-revision-v1','','','2019-03-15 02:01:15','2019-03-15 02:01:15','',213,'http://waseemorphali.com/213-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(256,1,'2019-03-15 02:01:30','2019-03-15 02:01:30','<p>We built a system that sees the position of a toy car using a camera fixed to the ceiling and drives it automatically to the desired location.</p><p>We coded the system in MATLAB. We used image processing to identify the car\'s position and destination and we coded 3 different methods of control to guide the car to the destination.</p><p>The image processing technique we used was background subtraction. This method easily detects the car since it\'s the only object moving in the environment. A Gaussian filter was applied to reduce the noise after subtraction and then a threshold was applied and the remaining pixel locations was averaged to get the car\'s location. The process is shown below.</p>		\n				<figure><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Car.png\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"1fe0c25\" data-elementor-lightbox-index=\"0\"><img src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Car.png\" alt=\"Car\" /></a><figcaption>Car</figcaption></figure><figure><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/car2.png\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"1fe0c25\" data-elementor-lightbox-index=\"1\"><img src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/car2.png\" alt=\"Subtracted Background\" /></a><figcaption>Subtracted Background</figcaption></figure><figure><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/car3.png\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"1fe0c25\" data-elementor-lightbox-index=\"2\"><img src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/car3.png\" alt=\"Gaussian Filter\" /></a><figcaption>Gaussian Filter</figcaption></figure><figure><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/car4.png\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"1fe0c25\" data-elementor-lightbox-index=\"3\"><img src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/car4.png\" alt=\"Threshold Applied\" /></a><figcaption>Threshold Applied</figcaption></figure>			\n		<p>We used a cheap remote controlled toy car we bought from the local market and we modified its motor because it was too fast to be controlled accurately.</p>		\n											<a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Car.jpg\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\">\n							<img width=\"300\" height=\"225\" src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Car-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Car-300x225.jpg 300w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Car-768x576.jpg 768w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Car-1024x768.jpg 1024w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Car.jpg 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" />								</a>','Visually Servoed RC Toy Car','','inherit','closed','closed','','213-revision-v1','','','2019-03-15 02:01:30','2019-03-15 02:01:30','',213,'http://waseemorphali.com/213-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(261,1,'2019-03-15 02:26:52','2019-03-15 02:26:52','<p>We built a system that sees the position of a toy car using a camera fixed to the ceiling and drives it automatically to the desired location.</p><p>We coded the system in MATLAB. We used image processing to identify the car\'s position and destination and we coded 3 different methods of control to guide the car to the destination.</p><p>The image processing technique we used was background subtraction. This method easily detects the car since it\'s the only object moving in the environment. A Gaussian filter was applied to reduce the noise after subtraction and then a threshold was applied and the remaining pixel locations was averaged to get the car\'s location. The process is shown below.</p>		\n				<figure><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Car.png\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"1fe0c25\" data-elementor-lightbox-index=\"0\"><img src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Car.png\" alt=\"Car\" /></a><figcaption>Car</figcaption></figure><figure><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/car2.png\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"1fe0c25\" data-elementor-lightbox-index=\"1\"><img src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/car2.png\" alt=\"Subtracted Background\" /></a><figcaption>Subtracted Background</figcaption></figure><figure><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/car3.png\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"1fe0c25\" data-elementor-lightbox-index=\"2\"><img src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/car3.png\" alt=\"Gaussian Filter\" /></a><figcaption>Gaussian Filter</figcaption></figure><figure><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/car4.png\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"1fe0c25\" data-elementor-lightbox-index=\"3\"><img src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/car4.png\" alt=\"Threshold Applied\" /></a><figcaption>Threshold Applied</figcaption></figure>			\n		<p>We used a cheap remote controlled toy car we bought from the local market and we modified its motor because it was too fast to be controlled accurately.</p>		\n											<a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Car.jpg\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\">\n							<img width=\"300\" height=\"225\" src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Car-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Car-300x225.jpg 300w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Car-768x576.jpg 768w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Car-1024x768.jpg 1024w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Car.jpg 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" />								</a>\n		<p>To control the car we hacked its remote controller and made our own printed circuit board (PCB) so that we can connect the PC to the remote controller.</p>		\n				<figure><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/20151109_161717-e1552616478298.jpg\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"f7c4b26\" data-elementor-lightbox-index=\"0\"><img src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/20151109_161717-e1552616478298-768x1024.jpg\" alt=\"20151109_161717\" /></a></figure><figure><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/IMG-20151109-WA0002-e1552616585742.jpeg\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"f7c4b26\" data-elementor-lightbox-index=\"1\"><img src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/IMG-20151109-WA0002-e1552616585742-768x1365.jpeg\" alt=\"IMG-20151109-WA0002\" /></a></figure>','Visually Servoed RC Toy Car','','inherit','closed','closed','','213-revision-v1','','','2019-03-15 02:26:52','2019-03-15 02:26:52','',213,'http://waseemorphali.com/213-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(259,1,'2019-03-15 02:20:57','2019-03-15 02:20:57','','20151109_161717','','inherit','open','closed','','20151109_161717','','','2019-03-15 02:21:48','2019-03-15 02:21:48','',213,'http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/20151109_161717.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(260,1,'2019-03-15 02:21:01','2019-03-15 02:21:01','','IMG-20151109-WA0002','','inherit','open','closed','','img-20151109-wa0002','','','2019-03-15 02:21:01','2019-03-15 02:21:01','',213,'http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/IMG-20151109-WA0002.jpeg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(262,1,'2019-03-15 02:34:05','2019-03-15 02:34:05','','Project Poster','','inherit','open','closed','','project-poster','','','2019-03-15 02:34:05','2019-03-15 02:34:05','',213,'http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Project-Poster.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(263,1,'2019-03-15 02:34:16','2019-03-15 02:34:16','<p>We built a system that sees the position of a toy car using a camera fixed to the ceiling and drives it automatically to the desired location.</p><p>We coded the system in MATLAB. We used image processing to identify the car\'s position and destination and we coded 3 different methods of control to guide the car to the destination.</p><p>The image processing technique we used was background subtraction. This method easily detects the car since it\'s the only object moving in the environment. A Gaussian filter was applied to reduce the noise after subtraction and then a threshold was applied and the remaining pixel locations was averaged to get the car\'s location. The process is shown below.</p>		\n				<figure><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Car.png\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"1fe0c25\" data-elementor-lightbox-index=\"0\"><img src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Car.png\" alt=\"Car\" /></a><figcaption>Car</figcaption></figure><figure><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/car2.png\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"1fe0c25\" data-elementor-lightbox-index=\"1\"><img src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/car2.png\" alt=\"Subtracted Background\" /></a><figcaption>Subtracted Background</figcaption></figure><figure><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/car3.png\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"1fe0c25\" data-elementor-lightbox-index=\"2\"><img src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/car3.png\" alt=\"Gaussian Filter\" /></a><figcaption>Gaussian Filter</figcaption></figure><figure><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/car4.png\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"1fe0c25\" data-elementor-lightbox-index=\"3\"><img src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/car4.png\" alt=\"Threshold Applied\" /></a><figcaption>Threshold Applied</figcaption></figure>			\n		<p>We used a cheap remote controlled toy car we bought from the local market and we modified its motor because it was too fast to be controlled accurately.</p>		\n											<a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Car.jpg\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\">\n							<img width=\"300\" height=\"225\" src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Car-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Car-300x225.jpg 300w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Car-768x576.jpg 768w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Car-1024x768.jpg 1024w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Car.jpg 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" />								</a>\n		<p>To control the car we hacked its remote controller and made our own printed circuit board (PCB) so that we can connect the PC to the remote controller.</p>		\n				<figure><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/20151109_161717-e1552616478298.jpg\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"f7c4b26\" data-elementor-lightbox-index=\"0\"><img src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/20151109_161717-e1552616478298-768x1024.jpg\" alt=\"20151109_161717\" /></a></figure><figure><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/IMG-20151109-WA0002-e1552616585742.jpeg\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"f7c4b26\" data-elementor-lightbox-index=\"1\"><img src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/IMG-20151109-WA0002-e1552616585742-768x1365.jpeg\" alt=\"IMG-20151109-WA0002\" /></a></figure>			\n		<p>The project was completed successfully and the system was able to control the car perfectly.</p><p>Shown below is the project poster.</p>		\n										<img width=\"620\" height=\"438\" src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Project-Poster-1024x723.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Project-Poster-1024x723.jpg 1024w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Project-Poster-300x212.jpg 300w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Project-Poster-768x543.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" />','Visually Servoed RC Toy Car','','inherit','closed','closed','','213-revision-v1','','','2019-03-15 02:34:16','2019-03-15 02:34:16','',213,'http://waseemorphali.com/213-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(264,1,'2019-03-15 02:34:24','2019-03-15 02:34:24','<p>We built a system that sees the position of a toy car using a camera fixed to the ceiling and drives it automatically to the desired location.</p><p>We coded the system in MATLAB. We used image processing to identify the car\'s position and destination and we coded 3 different methods of control to guide the car to the destination.</p><p>The image processing technique we used was background subtraction. This method easily detects the car since it\'s the only object moving in the environment. A Gaussian filter was applied to reduce the noise after subtraction and then a threshold was applied and the remaining pixel locations was averaged to get the car\'s location. The process is shown below.</p>		\n				<figure><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Car.png\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"1fe0c25\" data-elementor-lightbox-index=\"0\"><img src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Car.png\" alt=\"Car\" /></a><figcaption>Car</figcaption></figure><figure><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/car2.png\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"1fe0c25\" data-elementor-lightbox-index=\"1\"><img src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/car2.png\" alt=\"Subtracted Background\" /></a><figcaption>Subtracted Background</figcaption></figure><figure><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/car3.png\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"1fe0c25\" data-elementor-lightbox-index=\"2\"><img src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/car3.png\" alt=\"Gaussian Filter\" /></a><figcaption>Gaussian Filter</figcaption></figure><figure><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/car4.png\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"1fe0c25\" data-elementor-lightbox-index=\"3\"><img src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/car4.png\" alt=\"Threshold Applied\" /></a><figcaption>Threshold Applied</figcaption></figure>			\n		<p>We used a cheap remote controlled toy car we bought from the local market and we modified its motor because it was too fast to be controlled accurately.</p>		\n											<a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Car.jpg\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\">\n							<img width=\"300\" height=\"225\" src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Car-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Car-300x225.jpg 300w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Car-768x576.jpg 768w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Car-1024x768.jpg 1024w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Car.jpg 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" />								</a>\n		<p>To control the car we hacked its remote controller and made our own printed circuit board (PCB) so that we can connect the PC to the remote controller.</p>		\n				<figure><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/20151109_161717-e1552616478298.jpg\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"f7c4b26\" data-elementor-lightbox-index=\"0\"><img src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/20151109_161717-e1552616478298-768x1024.jpg\" alt=\"20151109_161717\" /></a></figure><figure><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/IMG-20151109-WA0002-e1552616585742.jpeg\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"f7c4b26\" data-elementor-lightbox-index=\"1\"><img src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/IMG-20151109-WA0002-e1552616585742-768x1365.jpeg\" alt=\"IMG-20151109-WA0002\" /></a></figure>			\n		<p>The project was completed successfully and the system was able to control the car perfectly.</p><p>Shown below is the project poster.</p>		\n											<a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Project-Poster.jpg\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\">\n							<img width=\"620\" height=\"438\" src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Project-Poster-1024x723.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Project-Poster-1024x723.jpg 1024w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Project-Poster-300x212.jpg 300w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Project-Poster-768x543.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" />								</a>','Visually Servoed RC Toy Car','','inherit','closed','closed','','213-revision-v1','','','2019-03-15 02:34:24','2019-03-15 02:34:24','',213,'http://waseemorphali.com/213-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(265,1,'2019-03-15 02:35:05','2019-03-15 02:35:05','<p>We built a system that sees the position of a toy car using a camera fixed to the ceiling and drives it automatically to the desired location.</p><p>We coded the system in MATLAB. We used image processing to identify the car\'s position and destination and we coded 3 different methods of control to guide the car to the destination.</p><p>The image processing technique we used was background subtraction. This method easily detects the car since it\'s the only object moving in the environment. A Gaussian filter was applied to reduce the noise after subtraction and then a threshold was applied and the remaining pixel locations was averaged to get the car\'s location. The process is shown below.</p>		\n				<figure><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Car.png\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"1fe0c25\" data-elementor-lightbox-index=\"0\"><img src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Car.png\" alt=\"Car\" /></a><figcaption>Car</figcaption></figure><figure><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/car2.png\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"1fe0c25\" data-elementor-lightbox-index=\"1\"><img src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/car2.png\" alt=\"Subtracted Background\" /></a><figcaption>Subtracted Background</figcaption></figure><figure><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/car3.png\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"1fe0c25\" data-elementor-lightbox-index=\"2\"><img src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/car3.png\" alt=\"Gaussian Filter\" /></a><figcaption>Gaussian Filter</figcaption></figure><figure><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/car4.png\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"1fe0c25\" data-elementor-lightbox-index=\"3\"><img src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/car4.png\" alt=\"Threshold Applied\" /></a><figcaption>Threshold Applied</figcaption></figure>			\n		<p>We used a cheap remote controlled toy car we bought from the local market and we modified its motor because it was too fast to be controlled accurately.</p>		\n											<a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Car.jpg\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\">\n							<img width=\"300\" height=\"225\" src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Car-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Car-300x225.jpg 300w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Car-768x576.jpg 768w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Car-1024x768.jpg 1024w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Car.jpg 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" />								</a>\n		<p>To control the car we hacked its remote controller and made our own printed circuit board (PCB) so that we can connect the PC to the remote controller.</p>		\n				<figure><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/20151109_161717-e1552616478298.jpg\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"f7c4b26\" data-elementor-lightbox-index=\"0\"><img src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/20151109_161717-e1552616478298-768x1024.jpg\" alt=\"20151109_161717\" /></a></figure><figure><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/IMG-20151109-WA0002-e1552616585742.jpeg\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"f7c4b26\" data-elementor-lightbox-index=\"1\"><img src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/IMG-20151109-WA0002-e1552616585742-768x1365.jpeg\" alt=\"IMG-20151109-WA0002\" /></a></figure>			\n		<p>The project was completed successfully and the system was able to control the car perfectly.</p><p>Shown below is the project poster.</p>		\n											<a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Project-Poster.jpg\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\">\n							<img width=\"3179\" height=\"2246\" src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Project-Poster.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Project-Poster.jpg 3179w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Project-Poster-300x212.jpg 300w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Project-Poster-768x543.jpg 768w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/Project-Poster-1024x723.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 3179px) 100vw, 3179px\" />								</a>','Visually Servoed RC Toy Car','','inherit','closed','closed','','213-revision-v1','','','2019-03-15 02:35:05','2019-03-15 02:35:05','',213,'http://waseemorphali.com/213-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(300,1,'2019-07-30 14:30:43','2019-07-30 14:30:43','<h2><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/education/\">Education</a></h2>		\n			<figure><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/education/#Bsc\"><img width=\"225\" height=\"225\" src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/download.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/download.png 225w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/download-150x150.png 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 225px) 100vw, 225px\" /></a></figure><h3><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/education/#Bsc\">Bsc. Electrical Engineering</a></h3><p>King Fahd University of Petroleum and Minerals</p>		\n			<figure><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/education/#Msc\"><img width=\"1272\" height=\"524\" src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Logo_of_New_Jersey_Institute_of_Technology.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Logo_of_New_Jersey_Institute_of_Technology.png 1272w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Logo_of_New_Jersey_Institute_of_Technology-300x124.png 300w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Logo_of_New_Jersey_Institute_of_Technology-768x316.png 768w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Logo_of_New_Jersey_Institute_of_Technology-1024x422.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1272px) 100vw, 1272px\" /></a></figure><h3><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/education/#Msc\">Msc. Electrical Engineering</a></h3><p>New Jersey Institute of Technology</p>		\n			<h2><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/experience/\">Experience</a></h2>		\n			<h2><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/experience/\">Senior Coach</a></h2>		\n			<h2><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/experience/#2\">Student Associate</a></h2>		\n			<h2><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/experience/#3\">Intern</a></h2>		\n		<p>                   Jan 2019 - Present</p><p>                   July 2018 - Dec 2018</p><p>                   June 2015 - Aug 2015</p>		\n			<h2><p id=\"Projects\">Projects</p></h2>		\n												<a href=\"\">Implementation of Cyclic Redundancy Check on FPGA</a>\n					<p>Dec 2018</p><p><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/implementation-of-cyclic-redundancy-check-on-fpga/\">Click here</a></p><p>I implemented three Cyclic Redundancy Check algorithms (CRC-8 , CRC-5 , CRC-3) on Intle&#8217;s FPGA board DE2-70 using VHDL.</p>\n												<a href=\"\">Implementation of Tree Pattern Matching</a>\n					<p>May 2018</p><p><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/implementation-of-tree-pattern-matching/\">Click Here</a></p><p>We implemented an algorithm for tree pattern matching described in the IEEE paper &#8220;A Parallel Algorithm and Architecture for Object Recognition in Images&#8221;.</p><p>We used VHDL to implement the algorithm, and we added our own designed components to control data flow through the circuit.</p>\n												<a href=\"\">Design of a Wearable Augmented Reality System</a>\n					<p>May 2017</p><p>Designed a simple augmented reality system using available components in the market.</p>\n												<a href=\"\">Visually Servoed RC Toy Car</a>\n					<p>Dec 2015</p><p><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/visually-servoed-rc-toy-car/\">Click Here</a></p><p>It was my capstone project for my undergraduate degree. We built a system that senses the position of a toy car and drives it automatically to the desired location through a PC.</p>\n												<a href=\"\">Power System Design and Analysis</a>\n					<p>May 2015</p><p>Learned how to use ETAP software and designed a simple power network and analyzed it.</p>\n			<h2><p id=\"Skills\">Skills</p></h2>		\n		<ul><li>Microsoft Office Suite</li><li>C</li><li>Python</li><li>Matlab</li><li>Assembly</li><li>VHDL</li></ul><ul><li>Mentor Graphics</li><li>HSPICE</li><li>PLC Programming</li><li>Arduino</li><li>Fusion 360</li><li>Languages: English, Arabic, Spanish (elementary)</li></ul>','Home','','inherit','closed','closed','','11-revision-v1','','','2019-07-30 14:30:43','2019-07-30 14:30:43','',11,'http://waseemorphali.com/11-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(268,1,'2019-03-15 14:11:46','2019-03-15 14:11:46','<h2><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/education/\">Education</a></h2>		\n			<figure><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/education/#Bsc\"><img width=\"225\" height=\"225\" src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/download.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/download.png 225w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/download-150x150.png 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 225px) 100vw, 225px\" /></a></figure><h3><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/education/#Bsc\">Bsc. Electrical Engineering</a></h3><p>King Fahd University of Petroleum and Minerals</p>		\n			<figure><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/education/#Msc\"><img width=\"1272\" height=\"524\" src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Logo_of_New_Jersey_Institute_of_Technology.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Logo_of_New_Jersey_Institute_of_Technology.png 1272w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Logo_of_New_Jersey_Institute_of_Technology-300x124.png 300w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Logo_of_New_Jersey_Institute_of_Technology-768x316.png 768w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Logo_of_New_Jersey_Institute_of_Technology-1024x422.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1272px) 100vw, 1272px\" /></a></figure><h3><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/education/#Msc\">Msc. Electrical Engineering</a></h3><p>New Jersey Institute of Technology</p>		\n			<h2><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/experience/\">Experience</a></h2>','Home','','inherit','closed','closed','','11-revision-v1','','','2019-03-15 14:11:46','2019-03-15 14:11:46','',11,'http://waseemorphali.com/11-