t Recognition in Images&#8221;.</p><p>We used VHDL to implement the algorithm, and we added our own designed components to control data flow through the circuit.</p>\n												<a href=\"\">Design of a Wearable Augmented Reality System</a>\n					<p>May 2017</p><p>Designed a simple augmented reality system using available components in the market.</p>\n												<a href=\"\">Visually Servoed RC Toy Car</a>\n					<p>Dec 2015</p><p><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/visually-servoed-rc-toy-car/\">Click Here</a></p><p>It was my capstone project for my undergraduate degree. We built a system that senses the position of a toy car and drives it automatically to the desired location through a PC.</p>\n												<a href=\"\">Power System Design and Analysis</a>\n					<p>May 2015</p><p>Learned how to use ETAP software and designed a simple power network and analyzed it. </p>\n			<h2><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/projects/\">Skills</a></h2>		\n		<ul><li>Microsoft Office Suite</li><li>C</li><li>Python</li><li>Matlab</li><li>Assembly</li><li>VHDL</li></ul><ul><li>Mentor Graphics</li><li>HSPICE</li><li>PLC Programming</li><li>Arduino</li><li>Fusion 360</li><li>Languages: English, Arabic, Spanish (elementary)</li></ul>','Home','','inherit','closed','closed','','11-revision-v1','','','2019-03-15 14:42:58','2019-03-15 14:42:58','',11,'http://waseemorphali.com/11-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(279,1,'2019-03-15 14:44:58','2019-03-15 14:44:58','A&nbsp;<b>cyclic redundancy check</b>&nbsp;(<b>CRC</b>) is an&nbsp;error-detecting code&nbsp;commonly used in digital&nbsp;networks&nbsp;and storage devices to detect accidental changes to raw data. Blocks of data entering these systems get a short&nbsp;<i>check value</i>&nbsp;attached, based on the remainder of a&nbsp;polynomial division&nbsp;of their contents. On retrieval, the calculation is repeated and, in the event the check values do not match, corrective action can be taken against data corruption. (<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cyclic_redundancy_check\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Wikipedia</a>)\n\nI wrote a VHDL code to simulate user input as a number of bits and shows the output with the CRC code attached on the LEDs of the intel DE2-70\n<figure>\n										<img width=\"620\" height=\"146\" src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/CRC1-Diagram.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/CRC1-Diagram.png 676w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/CRC1-Diagram-300x71.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\"><figcaption>Implementation of CRC-3</figcaption></figure>\n<figure>\n										<img width=\"620\" height=\"108\" src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/CRC0-Diagram-1024x178.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/CRC0-Diagram-1024x178.png 1024w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/CRC0-Diagram-300x52.png 300w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/CRC0-Diagram-768x134.png 768w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/CRC0-Diagram.png 1119w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\">\n\n<figcaption>Implementation of CRC-5</figcaption></figure>\n<figure>\n										<img width=\"620\" height=\"79\" src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/CRC2-Diagram-1024x131.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/CRC2-Diagram-1024x131.png 1024w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/CRC2-Diagram-300x38.png 300w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/CRC2-Diagram-768x98.png 768w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/CRC2-Diagram.png 1326w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\">\n\n<figcaption>Implementation of CRC-8</figcaption></figure>\nI simulated the circuit using the software from Intel called Quartus and showed how it works perfectly as inteded:\n<figure>\n										<img width=\"620\" height=\"112\" src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/crc0-simulation-1024x185.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/crc0-simulation-1024x185.jpg 1024w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/crc0-simulation-300x54.jpg 300w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/crc0-simulation-768x139.jpg 768w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/crc0-simulation.jpg 1072w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\">\n\n<figcaption>crc0 shows the CRC-3 code to be attached</figcaption></figure>\n<figure>\n										<img width=\"620\" height=\"110\" src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/crc1-simulation-1024x182.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/crc1-simulation-1024x182.jpg 1024w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/crc1-simulation-300x53.jpg 300w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/crc1-simulation-768x137.jpg 768w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/crc1-simulation.jpg 1100w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\">\n\n<figcaption>crc1 shows the CRC-5 code to be attached</figcaption></figure>\n<figure>\n										<img width=\"620\" height=\"112\" src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/crc2-simulation-1024x185.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/crc2-simulation-1024x185.jpg 1024w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/crc2-simulation-300x54.jpg 300w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/crc2-simulation-768x139.jpg 768w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/crc2-simulation.jpg 1082w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\">\n\n<figcaption>crc2 shows the CRC-8 code to be attached</figcaption></figure>\nI presented the circuit and code to the professor and demonstrated the how the code works on the DE2-70 board\n\n<img width=\"620\" height=\"349\" src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/20181217_115414-1024x576.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/20181217_115414-1024x576.jpg 1024w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/20181217_115414-300x169.jpg 300w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/20181217_115414-768x432.jpg 768w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/20181217_115414-520x292.jpg 520w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/20181217_115414-720x404.jpg 720w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\">','Implementation of Cyclic Redundancy Check on FPGA','','inherit','closed','closed','','209-autosave-v1','','','2019-03-15 14:44:58','2019-03-15 14:44:58','',209,'http://waseemorphali.com/209-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(282,1,'2019-03-15 14:57:59','2019-03-15 14:57:59','','Projects','','publish','closed','closed','','projects','','','2019-03-15 15:03:52','2019-03-15 15:03:52','',0,'http://waseemorphali.com/projects/',4,'nav_menu_item','',0),(283,1,'2019-03-15 14:57:59','2019-03-15 14:57:59',' ','','','publish','closed','closed','','283','','','2019-03-15 14:57:59','2019-03-15 14:57:59','',0,'http://waseemorphali.com/283/',1,'nav_menu_item','',0),(287,1,'2019-03-15 15:00:57','2019-03-15 15:00:57','','Skills','','publish','closed','closed','','skills','','','2019-03-15 15:04:23','2019-03-15 15:04:23','',0,'http://waseemorphali.com/skills/',5,'nav_menu_item','',0),(288,1,'2019-03-15 15:02:15','2019-03-15 15:02:15','<h2><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/education/\">Education</a></h2>		\n			<figure><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/education/#Bsc\"><img width=\"225\" height=\"225\" src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/download.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/download.png 225w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/download-150x150.png 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 225px) 100vw, 225px\" /></a></figure><h3><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/education/#Bsc\">Bsc.