ay 2018</p><p><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/implementation-of-tree-pattern-matching/\">Click Here</a></p><p>We implemented an algorithm for tree pattern matching described in the IEEE paper &#8220;A Parallel Algorithm and Architecture for Object Recognition in Images&#8221;.</p><p>We used VHDL to implement the algorithm, and we added our own designed components to control data flow through the circuit.</p>\n												<a href=\"\">Design of a Wearable Augmented Reality System</a>\n					<p>May 2017</p><p>Designed a simple augmented reality system using available components in the market.</p>\n												<a href=\"\">Visually Servoed RC Toy Car</a>\n					<p>Dec 2015</p><p><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/visually-servoed-rc-toy-car/\">Click Here</a></p><p>It was my capstone project for my undergraduate degree. We built a system that senses the position of a toy car and drives it automatically to the desired location through a PC.</p>\n												<a href=\"\">Power System Design and Analysis</a>\n					<p>May 2015</p><p>Learned how to use ETAP software and designed a simple power network and analyzed it.</p>\n			<h2><p id=\"Skills\">Skills</p></h2>		\n		<ul><li>Microsoft Office Suite</li><li>C</li><li>Python</li><li>Matlab</li><li>Assembly</li><li>VHDL</li></ul><ul><li>Mentor Graphics</li><li>HSPICE</li><li>PLC Programming</li><li>Arduino</li><li>Fusion 360</li><li>Languages: English, Arabic, Spanish (elementary)</li></ul>','Home','','inherit','closed','closed','','11-revision-v1','','','2019-03-15 15:03:36','2019-03-15 15:03:36','',11,'http://waseemorphali.com/11-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(302,1,'2019-12-30 23:36:46','2019-12-30 23:36:46','<h2>\n<p id=\"1\">Senior Coach</p>\n</h2>\n<strong>TechGarage, Boca Raton, FL</strong>\n\nJan 2019 - Present\n<figure><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/20190228_113916-e1552241406294.jpg\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"93af0a1\" data-elementor-lightbox-index=\"0\"><img src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/20190228_113916-320x320.jpg\" alt=\"20190228_113916\"></a></figure>\n<figure><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/20190228_120627-e1552241735258.jpg\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"93af0a1\" data-elementor-lightbox-index=\"1\"><img src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/20190228_120627-e1552241699407-320x320.jpg\" alt=\"20190228_120627\"></a></figure>\n<figure><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/20190302_111425-e1552241714119.jpg\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"93af0a1\" data-elementor-lightbox-index=\"2\"><img src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/20190302_111425-320x320.jpg\" alt=\"20190302_111425\"></a></figure>\n<figure><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/IMG_7862.jpg\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"93af0a1\" data-elementor-lightbox-index=\"3\"><img src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/IMG_7862-320x320.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_7862\"></a></figure>\n<ul>\n 	<li>I coach students enrolled in the program on coding, Arduino, 3-D modeling and printing and tech.</li>\n 	<li>I supervise and train 3 junior coaches.</li>\n 	<li>I mentored a group of high school students building a robot to compete in FIRST Robotics Competition (FRC) 2019.</li>\n 	<li>Shown in the pictures is the team of students I coached for FRC 2019.</li>\n 	<li>Also shown is the ramp robot that we built for the competition.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>\n<p id=\"2\">Student Associate</p>\n</h2>\n<strong>NJIT Strategic Events and Conference Services, Newark, NJ</strong>\n\nJuly 2018 - Dec 2018\n<figure><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/4.jpeg\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"73b26ac\" data-eleme