wanted to connect the AC thermostat in the house we are living in right now to the internet so we can control it through our phones instead of having to do it manually. So I designed and built a system to do that.</p><p>I designed a mechanical module with a servo motor that can be taped on the thermostat to control it, and I connected the servo motor to the ESP01 micro controller. ESP01 is an IOT micro controller that can be programmed using different methods, I programmed it using the Arduion IDE.</p><p>I used an APP called Blynk to to connect to the phone because it\'s free and it provides a very good GUI.</p><p>Since we are not the owners of the house, I didn\'t want to change anything in the wiring of the thermostat or do any permanent changes.</p>		\n				<figure><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/IMG_20191230_120557-e1577755298398.jpg\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"64a2157\" data-elementor-lightbox-index=\"0\"><img src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/IMG_20191230_120557-e1577755298398-320x320.jpg\" alt=\"Finished System\" /></a></figure><figure><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/IMG_20191230_120622-e1577755468609.jpg\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"64a2157\" data-elementor-lightbox-index=\"1\"><img src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/IMG_20191230_120622-e1577755468609-320x320.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_20191230_120622\" /></a></figure><figure><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/IMG_20191230_120713-e1577755480682.jpg\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"64a2157\" data-elementor-lightbox-index=\"2\"><img src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/IMG_20191230_120713-e1577755480682-320x320.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_20191230_120713\" /></a></figure>','WI-FI Enabled AC Thermostat','','inherit','closed','closed','','323-revision-v1','','','2019-12-31 01:29:01','2019-12-31 01:29:01','',323,'http://waseemorphali.com/323-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(336,1,'2019-12-31 01:33:06','2019-12-31 01:33:06','<h2><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/education/\">Education</a></h2>		\n			<figure><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/education/#Bsc\"><img width=\"225\" height=\"225\" src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/download.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/download.png 225w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/download-150x150.png 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 225px) 100vw, 225px\" /></a></figure><h3><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/education/#Bsc\">Bsc. Electrical Engineering</a></h3><p>King Fahd University of Petroleum and Minerals</p>		\n			<figure><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/education/#Msc\"><img width=\"1272\" height=\"524\" src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Logo_of_New_Jersey_Institute_of_Technology.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Logo_of_New_Jersey_Institute_of_Technology.png 1272w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Logo_of_New_Jersey_Institute_of_Technology-300x124.png 300w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Logo_of_New_Jersey_Institute_of_Technology-768x316.png 768w, http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/Logo_of_New_Jersey_Institute_of_Technology-1024x422.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1272px) 100vw, 1272px\" /></a></figure><h3><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/education/#Msc\">Msc. Electrical Engineering</a></h3><p>New Jersey Institute of Technology</p>		\n			<h2><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/experience/\">Experience</a></h2>		\n			<h2><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/experience/\">Senior Coach</a></h2>		\n			<h2><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/experience/#2\">Student Associate</a></h2>		\n			<h2><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/experience/#3\">Intern</a></h2>		\n		<p>                   Jan 2019 - Present</p><p>                   July 2018 - Dec 2018</p><p>                   June 2015 - Aug 2015</p>		\n			<h2><p id=\"Projects\">Projects</p></h2>		\n												<a href=\"\">Wi-Fi Enabled AC Thermostat</a>\n					<p>Nov 2019</p><p><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wi-fi-enabled-ac-thermostat/\">Click here</a></p><p>I built an interface for our old AC Thermostat so that it can be controlled using Wi-Fi.</p>\n												<a href=\"\">Chores Tracker using PIC16f88 MCU</a>\n					<p>Nov 2019</p><p><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/Chores-Tracker-using-pic16f88-mcu/\">Click here</a></p><p>I created  a system to keep track of chores in the house using a PIC16f88 micro controller. I programmed the micro controller in C.</p>\n												<a href=\"\">Implementation of Cyclic Redundancy Check on FPGA</a>\n					<p>Dec 2018</p><p><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/implementation-of-cyclic-redundancy-check-on-fpga/\">Click here</a></p><p>I implemented three Cyclic Redundancy Check algorithms (CRC-8 , CRC-5 , CRC-3) on Intle&#8217;s FPGA board DE2-70 using VHDL.</p>\n												<a href=\"\">Implementation of Tree Pattern Matching</a>\n					<p>May 2018</p><p><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/implementation-of-tree-pattern-matching/\">Click Here</a></p><p>We implemented an algorithm for tree pattern matching described in the IEEE paper &#8220;A Parallel Algorithm and Architecture for Object Recognition in Images&#8221;.</p><p>We used VHDL to implement the algorithm, and we added our own designed components to control data flow through the circuit.</p>\n												<a href=\"\">Design of a Wearable Augmented Reality System</a>\n					<p>May 2017</p><p>Designed a simple augmented reality system using available components in the market.</p>\n												<a href=\"\">Visually Servoed RC Toy Car</a>\n					<p>Dec 2015</p><p><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/visually-servoed-rc-toy-car/\">Click Here</a></p><p>It was my capstone project for my undergraduate degree. We built a system that senses the position of a toy car and drives it automatically to the desired location through a PC.</p>\n												<a href=\"\">Power System Design and Analysis</a>\n					<p>May 2015</p><p>Learned how to use ETAP software and designed a simple power network and analyzed it.</p>\n			<h2><p id=\"Skills\">Skills</p></h2>		\n		<ul><li>Microsoft Office Suite</li><li>C</li><li>Python</li><li>Matlab</li><li>Assembly</li><li>VHDL</li></ul><ul><li>Mentor Graphics</li><li>HSPICE</li><li>PLC Programming</li><li>Arduino</li><li>Fusion 360</li><li>Languages: English, Arabic, Spanish (elementary)</li></ul>','Home','','inherit','closed','closed','','11-revision-v1','','','2019-12-31 01:33:06','2019-12-31 01:33:06','',11,'http://waseemorphali.com/11-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(337,1,'2019-12-31 01:34:07','2019-12-31 01:34:07','I wanted to connect the AC thermostat in the house we are living in right now to the internet so we can control it through our phones instead of having to do it manually. So I designed and built a system to do that.\n\nI designed a mechanical module with a servo motor that can be taped on the thermostat to control it, and I connected the servo motor to the ESP01 micro controller. ESP01 is an IOT micro controller that can be programmed using different methods, I programmed it using the Arduion IDE.\n\nI used an APP called Blynk to to connect to the phone because it\'s free and it provides a very good GUI.\n\nSince we are not the owners of the house, I didn\'t want to change anything in the wiring of the thermostat or do any permanent changes.\n<figure><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/IMG_20191230_120557-e1577755298398.jpg\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"64a2157\" data-elementor-lightbox-index=\"0\"><img src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/IMG_20191230_120557-e1577755298398-320x320.jpg\" alt=\"Finished System\"></a></figure>\n<figure><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/IMG_20191230_120622-e1577755468609.jpg\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"64a2157\" data-elementor-lightbox-index=\"1\"><img src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/IMG_20191230_120622-e1577755468609-320x320.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_20191230_120622\"></a></figure>\n<figure><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/IMG_20191230_120713-e1577755480682.jpg\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"64a2157\" data-elementor-lightbox-index=\"2\"><img src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/IMG_20191230_120713-e1577755480682-320x320.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_20191230_120713\"></a></figure>','Wi-Fi Enabled AC Thermostat','','inherit','closed','closed','','323-revision-v1','','','2019-12-31 01:34:07','2019-12-31 01:34:07','',323,'http://waseemorphali.com/323-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(340,1,'2019-12-31 01:42:49','2019-12-31 01:42:49','<p>I wanted to connect the AC thermostat in the house we are living in right now to the internet so we can control it through our phones instead of having to do it manually. So I designed and built a system to do that.</p><p>I designed a mechanical module with a servo motor that can be taped on the thermostat to control it, and I connected the servo motor to the ESP01 micro controller. ESP01 is an IOT micro controller that can be programmed using different methods, I programmed it using the Arduion IDE.</p><p>I used an APP called Blynk to to connect to the phone because it\'s free and it provides a very good GUI.</p><p>Since we are not the owners of the house, I didn\'t want to change anything in the wiring of the thermostat or do any permanent changes.</p>		\n				<figure><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/IMG_20191230_120557-e1577755298398.jpg\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"64a2157\" data-elementor-lightbox-index=\"0\"><img src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/IMG_20191230_120557-e1577755298398-320x320.jpg\" alt=\"Finished System\" /></a></figure><figure><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/IMG_20191230_120622-e1577755468609.jpg\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"64a2157\" data-elementor-lightbox-index=\"1\"><img src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/IMG_20191230_120622-e1577755468609-320x320.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_20191230_120622\" /></a></figure><figure><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/IMG_20191230_120713-e1577755480682.jpg\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"64a2157\" data-elementor-lightbox-index=\"2\"><img src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/IMG_20191230_120713-e1577755480682-320x320.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_20191230_120713\" /></a></figure>			\n		<p>I got the gear and pinion design from a listing <a href=\"https://www.thingiverse.com/thing:3170748\">thingiverse</a> and I modified it to fit what I need. I also designed the enclosure for the electronics.</p>','Wi-Fi Enabled AC Thermostat','','inherit','closed','closed','','323-revision-v1','','','2019-12-31 01:42:49','2019-12-31 01:42:49','',323,'http://waseemorphali.com/323-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(339,1,'2019-12-31 01:41:06','2019-12-31 01:41:06','{{unknown}}','','','publish','closed','closed','','ff5a9ff7735c2a55f06a42463e9eabbf','','','2019-12-31 01:41:06','2019-12-31 01:41:06','',0,'http://waseemorphali.com/ff5a9ff7735c2a55f06a42463e9eabbf/',0,'oembed_cache','',0),(341,1,'2019-12-31 01:50:20','2019-12-31 01:50:20','','Motor Bracket and Pusher','Motor bracket and pusher','inherit','open','closed','','capture','','','2019-12-31 01:51:36','2019-12-31 01:51:36','',0,'http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Capture.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(344,1,'2019-12-31 01:53:56','2019-12-31 01:53:56','<p>I wanted to connect the AC thermostat in the house we are living in right now to the internet so we can control it through our phones instead of having to do it manually. So I designed and built a system to do that.</p><p>I designed a mechanical module with a servo motor that can be taped on the thermostat to control it, and I connected the servo motor to the ESP01 micro controller. ESP01 is an IOT micro controller that can be programmed using different methods, I programmed it using the Arduion IDE.</p><p>I used an APP called Blynk to to connect to the phone because it\'s free and it provides a very good GUI.</p><p>Since we are not the owners of the house, I didn\'t want to change anything in the wiring of the thermostat or do any permanent changes.</p>		\n				<figure><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/IMG_20191230_120557-e1577755298398.jpg\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"64a2157\" data-elementor-lightbox-index=\"0\"><img src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/IMG_20191230_120557-e1577755298398-320x320.jpg\" alt=\"Finished System\" /></a></figure><figure><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/IMG_20191230_120622-e1577755468609.jpg\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"64a2157\" data-elementor-lightbox-index=\"1\"><img src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/IMG_20191230_120622-e1577755468609-320x320.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_20191230_120622\" /></a></figure><figure><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/IMG_20191230_120713-e1577755480682.jpg\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"64a2157\" data-elementor-lightbox-index=\"2\"><img src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/IMG_20191230_120713-e1577755480682-320x320.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_20191230_120713\" /></a></figure>			\n		<p>I got the gear and pinion design from a listing <a href=\"https://www.thingiverse.com/thing:3170748\">thingiverse</a> and I modified it to fit what I need. I also designed the enclosure for the electronics.</p>		\n				<figure><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Capture2.png\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"b50fd65\" data-elementor-lightbox-index=\"0\"><img src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Capture2-320x320.png\" alt=\"Electronics housing\" /></a></figure><figure><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Capture.png\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"b50fd65\" data-elementor-lightbox-index=\"1\"><img src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Capture-320x320.png\" alt=\"Motor bracket and pusher\" /></a></figure>','Wi-Fi Enabled AC Thermostat','','inherit','closed','closed','','323-revision-v1','','','2019-12-31 01:53:56','2019-12-31 01:53:56','',323,'http://waseemorphali.com/323-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(343,1,'2019-12-31 01:51:51','2019-12-31 01:51:51','','Electronics housing','Electronics housing','inherit','open','closed','','capture2','','','2019-12-31 01:52:09','2019-12-31 01:52:09','',0,'http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Capture2.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(345,1,'2019-12-31 01:55:07','2019-12-31 01:55:07','<p>I wanted to connect the AC thermostat in the house we are living in right now to the internet so we can control it through our phones instead of having to do it manually. So I designed and built a system to do that.</p><p>I designed a mechanical module with a servo motor that can be taped on the thermostat to control it, and I connected the servo motor to the ESP01 micro controller. ESP01 is an IOT micro controller that can be programmed using different methods, I programmed it using the Arduion IDE.</p><p>I used an APP called Blynk to to connect to the phone because it\'s free and it provides a very good GUI.</p><p>Since we are not the owners of the house, I didn\'t want to change anything in the wiring of the thermostat or do any permanent changes.</p>		\n				<figure><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/IMG_20191230_120557-e1577755298398.jpg\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"64a2157\" data-elementor-lightbox-index=\"0\"><img src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/IMG_20191230_120557-e1577755298398-320x320.jpg\" alt=\"Finished System\" /></a></figure><figure><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/IMG_20191230_120622-e1577755468609.jpg\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"64a2157\" data-elementor-lightbox-index=\"1\"><img src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/IMG_20191230_120622-e1577755468609-320x320.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_20191230_120622\" /></a></figure><figure><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/IMG_20191230_120713-e1577755480682.jpg\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"64a2157\" data-elementor-lightbox-index=\"2\"><img src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/IMG_20191230_120713-e1577755480682-320x320.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_20191230_120713\" /></a></figure>			\n		<p>I got the pinion gear and pusher design from a listing <a href=\"https://www.thingiverse.com/thing:3170748\">thingiverse</a> and I modified it to fit what I need. I also designed the enclosure for the electronics.</p>		\n				<figure><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Capture2.png\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"b50fd65\" data-elementor-lightbox-index=\"0\"><img src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Capture2-320x320.png\" alt=\"Electronics housing\" /></a></figure><figure><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Capture.png\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"b50fd65\" data-elementor-lightbox-index=\"1\"><img src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Capture-320x320.png\" alt=\"Motor bracket and pusher\" /></a></figure>','Wi-Fi Enabled AC Thermostat','','inherit','closed','closed','','323-revision-v1','','','2019-12-31 01:55:07','2019-12-31 01:55:07','',323,'http://waseemorphali.com/323-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(346,1,'2019-12-31 01:55:19','2019-12-31 01:55:19','<p>I wanted to connect the AC thermostat in the house we are living in right now to the internet so we can control it through our phones instead of having to do it manually. So I designed and built a system to do that.</p><p>I designed a mechanical module with a servo motor that can be taped on the thermostat to control it, and I connected the servo motor to the ESP01 micro controller. ESP01 is an IOT micro controller that can be programmed using different methods, I programmed it using the Arduion IDE.</p><p>I used an APP called Blynk to to connect to the phone because it\'s free and it provides a very good GUI.</p><p>Since we are not the owners of the house, I didn\'t want to change anything in the wiring of the thermostat or do any permanent changes.</p>		\n				<figure><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/IMG_20191230_120557-e1577755298398.jpg\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"64a2157\" data-elementor-lightbox-index=\"0\"><img src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/IMG_20191230_120557-e1577755298398-320x320.jpg\" alt=\"Finished System\" /></a></figure><figure><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/IMG_20191230_120622-e1577755468609.jpg\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"64a2157\" data-elementor-lightbox-index=\"1\"><img src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/IMG_20191230_120622-e1577755468609-320x320.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_20191230_120622\" /></a></figure><figure><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/IMG_20191230_120713-e1577755480682.jpg\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"64a2157\" data-elementor-lightbox-index=\"2\"><img src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/IMG_20191230_120713-e1577755480682-320x320.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_20191230_120713\" /></a></figure>			\n		<p>I got the pinion gear and pusher design from a listing on <a href=\"https://www.thingiverse.com/thing:3170748\">thingiverse</a> and I modified it to fit what I need. I also designed the enclosure for the electronics.</p>		\n				<figure><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Capture2.png\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"b50fd65\" data-elementor-lightbox-index=\"0\"><img src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Capture2-320x320.png\" alt=\"Electronics housing\" /></a></figure><figure><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Capture.png\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"b50fd65\" data-elementor-lightbox-index=\"1\"><img src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Capture-320x320.png\" alt=\"Motor bracket and pusher\" /></a></figure>','Wi-Fi Enabled AC Thermostat','','inherit','closed','closed','','323-revision-v1','','','2019-12-31 01:55:19','2019-12-31 01:55:19','',323,'http://waseemorphali.com/323-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(347,1,'2019-12-31 01:55:31','2019-12-31 01:55:31','<p>I wanted to connect the AC thermostat in the house we are living in right now to the internet so we can control it through our phones instead of having to do it manually. So I designed and built a system to do that.</p><p>I designed a mechanical module with a servo motor that can be taped on the thermostat to control it, and I connected the servo motor to the ESP01 micro controller. ESP01 is an IOT micro controller that can be programmed using different methods, I programmed it using the Arduion IDE.</p><p>I used an APP called Blynk to to connect to the phone because it\'s free and it provides a very good GUI.</p><p>Since we are not the owners of the house, I didn\'t want to change anything in the wiring of the thermostat or do any permanent changes.</p>		\n				<figure><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/IMG_20191230_120557-e1577755298398.jpg\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"64a2157\" data-elementor-lightbox-index=\"0\"><img src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/IMG_20191230_120557-e1577755298398-320x320.jpg\" alt=\"Finished System\" /></a></figure><figure><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/IMG_20191230_120622-e1577755468609.jpg\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"64a2157\" data-elementor-lightbox-index=\"1\"><img src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/IMG_20191230_120622-e1577755468609-320x320.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_20191230_120622\" /></a></figure><figure><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/IMG_20191230_120713-e1577755480682.jpg\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"64a2157\" data-elementor-lightbox-index=\"2\"><img src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/IMG_20191230_120713-e1577755480682-320x320.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_20191230_120713\" /></a></figure>			\n		<p>I got the pinion gear and pusher design from a listing on <a href=\"https://www.thingiverse.com/thing:3170748\">thingiverse</a> and I modified them to fit what I need. I also designed the enclosure for the electronics.</p>		\n				<figure><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Capture2.png\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"b50fd65\" data-elementor-lightbox-index=\"0\"><img src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Capture2-320x320.png\" alt=\"Electronics housing\" /></a></figure><figure><a href=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Capture.png\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"default\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"b50fd65\" data-elementor-lightbox-index=\"1\"><img src=\"http://waseemorphali.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/Capture-320x320.png\" alt=\"Motor bracket and pusher\" /></a></figure>','Wi-Fi Enabled AC Thermostat','','inherit','closed','closed','','323-revision-v1','','','2019-12-31 01:55:31','2019-12-31 01:55:31','',323,'http://waseemorphali.com/323-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0);
